INSERT INTO `golf` (`id`, `name`, `image`, `note`) VALUES
(1, 'Golf clubs for rent', 'Golf club for rent - Greentours.jpg', '<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"508\" src=\"/image/images/Greentours%20Indochina%20-%20Golf%20clubs%20for%20rent.PNG\" width=\"850\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Carrying a set of golf clubs during your journey can cause inconvenience and the shipping fee can be quite costly. Therefore, we provide the rental service with all kinds of golf clubs in different sizes to meet your requirements, including delivery service to your golf course.</p>\r\n'),
(2, 'Private golf pick up', 'Private golf car - Greentours.jpg', '<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"924\" src=\"/image/images/Greentours%20Indochina%20-%20Private%20golf%20pick%20up.jpg\" width=\"1500\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>We design transports customized to meet the need of golfers. Ones should feel comfortable with your seats while your golf clubs are taken care in spacious storage.</p>\r\n'),
(3, 'Local golfer interaction', 'Local golfer interaction - Greentours.jpg', '<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"800\" src=\"/image/images/Greentours%20Indochina%20-%20Local%20golfer%20interaction.jpg\" width=\"1200\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>We provide golf experience exchange and business opportunity seeking with local merchants.&nbsp;In Indochina, golfers are often successful businessmen. We can recommend different groups of golfers for you, where you can interact&nbsp;with one another and develop business opportunities with local merchants.</p>\r\n'),
(4, 'Tournaments registration', 'Golf cup - Greentours.jpg', '<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"533\" src=\"/image/images/Greentours%20Indochina%20-%20Local%20golf%20tournament.jpg\" width=\"800\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>We assist golfers in registering for local tournaments. If you are visiting a country and wish to interact with local golfers on your trip and on the occasion of a certain golf tournament, we can arrange for you to participate in and compete in those tournaments.</p>\r\n'),
(5, 'Cultural exchange', 'Golf culture exchange - Greentours.jpg', '<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"466\" src=\"/image/images/Greentours%20Indochina%20-%20Golf%20and%20cultural%20exchange.jpg\" width=\"700\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Golf tour can be combined with local cultural and culinary discovery.&nbsp;Other than providing golf services, we also organize golf tours combined with standard tours with a balanced itinerary to make your trip truly healthy and provide a deep insight into the culture of your chosen destination.</p>\r\n');

