(9, 5, 'vn', 'GREENTOURS sponsored Golf Championship major Q2 G&L 9295', 'The second largest Golf Tournament in 2019 of Vietnam\'s leading golf club G&L 9295 named after the sponsor - Greentours International, held at Tam Dao golf course on June 28.', '<h1 style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"color:#2c3e50\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">GREENTOURS sponsored Golf Championship major Q2 G&amp;L 9295</span></span></strong></h1>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">GreenTours International Championship - major Q2 G&amp;L 9295 took place successfully at Tam Dao golf course on June 28, 2019. At the awards ceremony, club members and benefactors have raised more than VND 50 million, supporting two members with difficulties&nbsp;of the 92-95 Hanoi community.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">This second largest golf tournament of G&amp;L 9295 in 2019 attracted 150 golfers, including club members and outside guests,&nbsp;competing&nbsp;together in many categories with a total award value of over VND 3 billion.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"591\" src=\"/image/images/Greentours%20charity%206.jpg\" width=\"1024\" /></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">In the evening, the award ceremony took place in a modern, G&amp;L-9295-Club style at the villa of the head of the organization board&nbsp;- Golfer Hoang Manh Hung - situated right&nbsp;next to Tam Dao golf course.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Exactly one year after winning the Q2 2018 major tournament on Yen Dung golf course, golfer La Huy Hoang continued the success to become the champion of the second largest tournament of the year G&amp;L 9295.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"663\" src=\"/image/images/Greentours%20charity%209.jpg\" width=\"1024\" /></span><img alt=\"\" height=\"663\" src=\"/image/images/Greentours%20Indochina%20responsible%20act%209.jpg\" width=\"1024\" /></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Beside&nbsp;the prize awarded to&nbsp;golfer La Huy Hoang, golfer&nbsp;Tran Trong Hieu, Duong Ho Minh, Duong Kim Trang, Huynh Ngoc Thuy consecutively&nbsp;topped the Clubs, Hole, Female and VIP category.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"719\" src=\"/image/images/Greentours%20charity%2010.jpg\" width=\"1024\" /><img alt=\"\" height=\"719\" src=\"/image/images/Greentours%20Indochina%20responsible%20act%2010.jpg\" width=\"1024\" /></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">At the awards gala, the club members, benefactors and guests have donated a total of more than VND 50 million to support two members of the Hanoi 92-95 community, including&nbsp;Nguyen Minh Duc, the son of Mr. Nguyen Minh Ha (former student of Yen Hoa school, year 92-95) who&nbsp;had lymphoma and Ms. Nguyen Thi Thu Hang (a member of Dinh Ty&nbsp;group).</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"738\" src=\"/image/images/Greentours%20charity%208.jpg\" width=\"1024\" /></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">This is a traditional activity of the G&amp;L Club 92-95 with the spirit of connecting friendship, sharing love and&nbsp;joining hands to support the community.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">G&amp;L 9295 Tour 2019 is the annual competition exclusively for members of the G&amp;L 9295 Club. The tournament is organized with the inspiration from&nbsp;FedEx Cup. Accordingly, the events will take place throughout 12 months of the year and a major tournament is held every quarter. The major prize will be named after the sponsor.</span></span></p>\r\n', '', '', '', '', '', 0, 'greentours-sponsored-golf-championship-major-q2-gl-9295', 'GREENTOURS sponsored Golf Championship major Q2 G&L 9295', 'The second largest Golf Tournament in 2019 of Vietnam\'s leading golf club G&L 9295 named after the sponsor - Greentours International, held at Tam Dao golf course on June 28.', 'Golf Tournament, Vietnam, Tam Dao golf course, golf club G&L 9295, Greentours International'),
(10, 5, 'en', 'english version Tuyển dụng: Vị trí nhân viên tư vấn visa', 'english version ', 'english version <p><strong>Do nhu cầu mở rộng kinh doanh, Greentours tuyển dụng th&ecirc;m 02 vị tr&iacute; nh&acirc;n vi&ecirc;n tư vấn visa. Mức lương từ 6 TRIỆU đồng đến kh&ocirc;ng giới hạn.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>M&ocirc; tả c&ocirc;ng việc:</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Tiếp nhận hồ sơ từ kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng.</li>\r\n	<li>Xử l&yacute; hồ sơ: Dịch thuật, thực hiện c&aacute;c form biểu mẫu, hướng dẫn kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng, hỗ trợ kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng book v&eacute; m&aacute;y bay, book kh&aacute;ch sạn&hellip;</li>\r\n	<li>Theo d&otilde;i qu&aacute; tr&igrave;nh ho&agrave;n tất hồ sơ xin visa, tư vấn v&agrave; hỗ trợ cho kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng.</li>\r\n	<li>Tiếp nhận v&agrave; đưa ra phương &aacute;n xử l&yacute; khiếu nại, giải đ&aacute;p thắc mắc của kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng, chuyển bộ phận li&ecirc;n quan.</li>\r\n	<li>C&aacute;c c&ocirc;ng việc kh&aacute;c được ph&acirc;n c&ocirc;ng bởi cấp tr&ecirc;n.</li>\r\n	<li>Trao đổi cụ thể khi phỏng vấn.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Y&ecirc;u cầu:</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Th&aacute;i độ chủ động, linh hoạt, ki&ecirc;n nhẫn, tự tin, cởi mở. Tư duy phục vụ. Khả năng l&agrave;m việc độc lập</li>\r\n	<li>Ưu ti&ecirc;n tốt nghiệp CĐ, ĐH chuy&ecirc;n ng&agrave;nh Kinh tế, thương mại, du lịch. C&aacute;c ứng vi&ecirc;n đ&atilde; từng l&agrave;m ở vị tr&iacute; tương đương, hoặc trong lĩnh vực du lịch, v&eacute; m&aacute;y bay</li>\r\n	<li>Kỹ năng giao tiếp v&agrave; đ&agrave;m ph&aacute;n tốt.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Quyền lợi:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Được l&agrave;m việc trong m&ocirc;i trường chuy&ecirc;n nghiệp với lịch sử 17 năm</li>\r\n	<li>Được&nbsp;chỉ bảo tận t&igrave;nh từ c&aacute;c anh chị c&oacute; nhiều năm kinh nghiệm</li>\r\n	<li>L&agrave;m việc hết m&igrave;nh vui chơi hết sức. L&agrave;m ra l&agrave;m chơi ra chơi, ăn uống quanh tuần. M&ocirc;i trường đồng nghiệp cực kỳ th&acirc;n thiện v&agrave; vui vẻ</li>\r\n	<li>Thưởng lớn nếu vượt chỉ ti&ecirc;u c&ocirc;ng việc. Được tăng lương hoặc cất nhắc l&ecirc;n trưởng bộ phận nếu l&agrave;m việc tốt.</li>\r\n	<li>Được hưởng&nbsp;BHXH v&agrave; c&aacute;c cơ chế hỗ trợ ăn trưa, đi lại, tiếp đ&oacute;n kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng... đầy đủ.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Ứng vi&ecirc;n quan t&acirc;m gửi CV k&egrave;m H&igrave;nh ảnh qua email:&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:hrmanager@greentours.com.vn\" target=\"_blank\">hrmanager@greentours.com.vn</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Hoặc li&ecirc;n hệ:&nbsp;<strong>0989.845.850</strong>&nbsp;(Mrs Hiền)</p>\r\n', '', '', '', '', '', 0, 'en-tuyen-dung-vi-tri-nhan-vien-tu-van-visa', 'Tuyển dụng: Vị trí nhân viên tư vấn visa', '', ''),
(11, 6, 'vn', 'GREENTOURS supported members of the Blind Association in Hai Duong', 'On January 28, 2019, the Board of Directors of Greentours JSC arrived in Thanh Mien district, Hai Duong province to present gifts for Tet Holiday to the members of the Blind Association who had a hard time making a living.', '<h1 style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"color:#2c3e50\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">GREENTOURS supported members of the Blind Association in Thanh Mien, Hai Duong</span></span></strong></h1>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#2c3e50\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Tet was coming and as every year, the Board of Directors of Greentours always paid close attention to charity programs. With the motto: &quot;Tet is sharing, warm spring is coming&quot;, Greentours always wished to provide people having difficulties throughout the country a better life.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#2c3e50\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">On this occasion, Greentours cooperated with the People&#39;s Committee of Thanh Mien District, Hai Duong Province to organize the program &quot;Gifts for Tet Holiday to members of the Blind Association of Thanh Mien District&quot;.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"900\" src=\"/image/images/Greentours%20charity%202.jpg\" width=\"1600\" /></span><img alt=\"\" height=\"900\" src=\"/image/images/Greentours%20cGreentours%20Indochina%20responsible%20act%202.jpg\" width=\"1600\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"color:#4e5f70\">Greentours presented a gift of VND 20,000,000 to the Blind Association in Thanh Mien District. This is a meaningful activity with the spirit of &ldquo;All for one, and one for all&quot; to encourage those who have unfortunate circumstances and help them overcome difficulties.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"color:#4e5f70\">To date, the Blind Association of Thanh Mien district has 283 members at all ages. Among them, there are 168 women, 15 children and 20 of them are wounded veterans. Most of the families are very poor and struggle hard to get by.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"color:#4e5f70\">Though what Greentours had to offer was very small in comparison to the difficulties these people had to face, Greentours sincerely hoped that our effort would support the members to reduce the inferiority complex and&nbsp;build up self-esteem for them to celebrate a happy Lunar New Year with the community and society.</span></span></p>\r\n', '', '', '', '', '', 0, 'greentours-supported-members-of-the-blind-association-in-hai-duong', 'GREENTOURS supported members of the Blind Association in Hai Duong', 'On January 28, 2019, the Board of Directors of Greentours JSC arrived in Thanh Mien district, Hai Duong province to present gifts for Tet Holiday to the members of the Blind Association who had a hard time making a living.', 'Greentours, social activity, responsible activity, voluntary, Blind Association, Hai Duong, Vietnam'),
(12, 6, 'en', 'english version Greentours supported member of the Blind Association in Thanh Mien District, Hai Duong Province for Tet Holiday', 'english version On January 28, 2019, the Board of Directors of Greentours JSC arrived in Thanh Mien district, Hai Duong province to present Tet gifts to the member of the Blind Association who had a hard time making a living.', 'english version <p>On this occasion, Greentours also cooperated with the People&#39;s Committee of Thanh Mien District, Hai Duong Province to organize the program &quot;Giving gifts to members of the Blind Association of Thanh Mien District on Tet Holiday&quot;.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"900\" src=\"/image/images/Greentours%20charity%202.jpg\" width=\"1600\" /></p>\r\n', '', '', '', '', '', 0, 'en-greentours-supported-member-of-the-blind-association-in-hai-duong', 'Greentours supported member of the Blind Association in Thanh Mien District, Hai Duong Province for Tet Holiday', '', ''),
(13, 7, 'vn', 'GREENTOURS presented gifts for poor households in Tan Loi commune', 'On January 16, 2019, Greentours cooperated with Thai Nguyen Provincial People\'s Committee, Dong Hy District People\'s Committee and Tan Loi Commune People\'s Committee to present gifts for Tet Holiday to poor households in Tan Loi commune.', '<h1 style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"color:#2c3e50\">GREENTOURS presented gifts for poor households in Tan Loi commune</span></span></strong></h1>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"color:#2c3e50\">To welcome the upcoming Tet Holiday and responding to the movement of &quot;Week for the Poor 2019&quot; of Thai Nguyen Province, Greentours&nbsp;had organized a voluntary program for&nbsp;the poor households&nbsp;in Thai Nguyen province to share part of their difficulties.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"color:#2c3e50\">In the cold&nbsp;drizzle throughout Thai Nguyen, we all dreamt&nbsp;of the warm spring approaching - The season of love. Greentours&nbsp; hoped that these gifts would bring&nbsp;warmth to the poor people in Tan Loc Commune, Dong Hy District, Thai Nguyen Province. With the message of&nbsp;&quot;Tet is sharing, warm spring is coming&quot;, the charitable activities always receive special attention from the Board of Director of Greentours every year.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><br />\r\n<img alt=\"\" height=\"960\" src=\"/image/images/Greentours%20Indochina%20responsible%20act%204.jpg\" width=\"1280\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"color:#2c3e50\">Shortly after the ceremony was held at the headquarters of the People&#39;s Committee of Tan Loi Commune, despite the cold weather and&nbsp;rugged roads, the Board of Directors of&nbsp;Greentours&nbsp;came to Cau Luu hamlet to deliver the gifts of&nbsp;VND 50,000,000 in cash for Ms.&nbsp;Vuong Thi Phuong&#39;s family, with the desire to bring them a new and stable home to welcome a warm and happy Tet Holiday. On that occation, Greentours also gave some gifts for Tet Holiday&nbsp;to other households in Tan Loi commune.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"color:#2c3e50\">Earlier on November 24, 2018, the representatives of Greentours visited the poor households in Bao Nang hamlet. After witnessing the difficult life of the locals, the Board of Director of Greentours&nbsp;decided to provide support in cash to build houses for a poverty-stricken family -&nbsp;Ms. Vuong Thi Phuong, a&nbsp;single mother.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"color:#2c3e50\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"960\" src=\"/image/images/Greentours%20charity%205.jpg\" width=\"1280\" /></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"color:#2c3e50\">These gifts however small, they carried in themselves&nbsp;a great meaning, which were the wishes of Greentours staff to people of Tan Loi commune, hoping that the unfortunate households would be able to welcome a warm, healthy and joyful Tet Holiday.</span></span></p>\r\n', '', '', '', '', '', 0, 'greentours-presented-gifts-for-poor-households-in-tan-loi-commune', 'GREENTOURS presented gifts for poor households in Tan Loi commune', 'Greentours cooperated with Thai Nguyen Provincial People\'s Committee, Dong Hy District People\'s Committee and Tan Loi Commune People\'s Committee to present gifts to poor households in Tan Loi commune, hoping that the unfortunate households would be able to welcome a warm and joyful Tet Holiday.', 'Greentours, voluntary, poor households, Thai Nguyen'),
(14, 7, 'en', 'english version GREENTOURS presented gifts for poor households in Tan Loi commune', 'english version ', 'english version ', '', '', '', '', '', 0, 'en-greentours-presented-gifts-for-poor-households-in-tan-loi-commune', 'GREENTOURS presented gifts for poor households in Tan Loi commune', '', '');

