(57, 46, 'vn', 'THE MANAGEMENT BOARD', '', '<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">Leaders of Greentours are all young, dynamic and dedicated to their jobs. Therefore, they have built Greentours to an energetic and youthful brand which always is a pioneer in exploring new destinations and leads the tourism market trends.&nbsp;Gradually the management board extend to international member from Korean to Australian and English. At Greentours, we accept the difference and turn new ideas to refresh the company and the itineraries of our dear travelers.</span></p>\r\n', '', '', '', '', '', 0, 'di-dung-ben-den-dung-gio', 'THE MANAGEMENT BOARD', '', ''),
