(13, 'VLCH - HIGHLIGHTS OF INDOCHINA', 'Admire the grandiose scenic beauty and experience an exciting adventure with the ultimate Indochina tour to explore Three countries in One exclusive trip.', '', '', '<h2 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\">The ultimate trip to explore Three countries in One destination</span></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Pull yourself away from the bustling daily life to seek for self-relaxation and let your mind wander with the clouds, to think less and feel more. Admire the beautiful scenery, the green primeval forests and go on an exciting adventure of your own. Participate in kayaking, cycling, hiking or interacting with the indigenous people. The simplicity, friendliness and hospitality that can be found anywhere in Indochina will make you eager to return for more.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n', '<h3 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">1. Please provide your full name exactly as per passport at the time of booking (including any middle names listed on your passport) for train and flight tickets.</span></h3>\r\n\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">2. A single supplement is available on this trip, subject to availability. Please contact your sales agent if you would like to book this.&nbsp;</span></h3>\r\n\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">3. This trip includes flight trips. Checked luggage allowance is a maximum 20kg, with up to 7kg carry on luggage. Any excess luggage charges will need to be paid directly to the airline at check-in.</span></h3>\r\n', '', 2768, 0, 0, 'HIGHLIGHTS-OF-INDOCHINA-Greentours-Indochina.jpg', '[\"{\\\"image\\\":\\\"DYNAMIC-OUTING-OF-THE-NORTH-Greentours-Indochina.jpg\\\"}\",\"{\\\"image\\\":\\\"Best-of-Cambodia-Greentours-Indochina.jpg\\\"}\"]', '2019-09-27 11:09:38', '2019-12-26 10:12:45', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '', '', '[\"2020-01-24\"]