(16, 'VCH - VIETNAM HERITAGE JOURNEY', 'An intriguing trip to discover relic of Vietnam’s history at must-see attractions in the central of Vietnam.', '', '', '<h2 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\">The ultimate Vietnam trip in the central region of Vietnam</span></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Discover the spirit of Vietnam on a trip in the central, taking in all the attractions in between. Explore Vietnam&#39;s historical attraction, beautiful landscapes, delicious cuisine and the renowned friendliness of the Vietnamese people.</span></p>\r\n', '<h3 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">1. Please provide your full name exactly as per passport at the time of booking (including any middle names listed on your passport).<br />\r\n2. A single supplement is available on this trip, subject to availability. Please contact your sales agent if you would like to book this.&nbsp;</span></h3>\r\n', '', 260, 0, 0, 'VIETNAM-HERITAGE-JOURNEY-Greentours-Indochina.jpg', '[\"{\\\"image\\\":\\\"Bana-hill-Greentours-Indochina.jpg\\\"}\",\"{\\\"image\\\":\\\"Da-Nang-Greentours-Indochina.jpg\\\"}\"]', '2019-09-27 11:09:17', '2019-12-26 10:12:22', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '', '', '[]', '', '', '', '', '', '6 breakfasts, 2 lunches', 'Private minibus, Private vehicle, Taxi', 'Hotel (6 nights)', 'Hoi An - Old Town walking tour\r\nHue - Imperial Citadel\r\nHue - Perfume River boat ride\r\nHue - Royal tomb of Emperor Tu Duc\r\nDa Nang - Relaxing at one of the most worth-living city', '', 1, 'VCH - VIETNAM HERITAGE JOURNEY', 'Discover the spirit of Vietnam on a trip in the central, taking in all the attractions in between. Explore Vietnam\'s attraction, beautiful landscapes, delicious cuisine and the hospitality of the locals with Vietnam tour package from Greentours Indochina.', 'vch-vietnam-heritage-journey', 'Vietnam tour, central Vietnam Greentours, Indochina', 1, '', 'Hue