(18, 'VCHC - HUE\'S SERENITY UNVEILED', 'As of today, there is no other region that can be on par with Hue, which possesses a large number of relics that still retain their inherent forms from the distant past.', '', '', '<h2 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\">Delve into the ancient charm of Hue</span></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Join a city tour around this ancient capital, which possesses a large number of relics that still retain their inherent forms from the distant past. Ride a bike to Pha Tam Giang, the&nbsp;famous for being the largest brackish water lagoon in Southeast Asia. Pha Tam Giang fascinates visitors by the wild beauty of the old fishing villages and the breath-taking view of the lagoon bathing in the spectacular sunset.&nbsp;Visit Thuy Lap craft village to learn about how the artisans create the products.</span></p>\r\n', '<h3 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">1. Please provide your full name exactly as per passport at the time of booking (including any middle names listed on your passport).<br />\r\n2. A single supplement is available on this trip, subject to availability. Please contact your sales agent if you would like to book this.&nbsp;</span></h3>\r\n', '', 305, 0, 0, 'HUE-SERENITY-UNVEILED-Greentours-Indochina.jpg', '[\"{\\\"image\\\":\\\"Hue-Greentours-Indochina.jpg\\\"}\",\"{\\\"image\\\":\\\"HIGHLIGHTS-OF-INDOCHINA-Greentours-Indochina.jpg\\\"}\"]', '2019-09-27 11:09:05', '2019-12-26 10:12:23', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '', '', '[]', '', '', '', '', '', '3 breakfasts, 2 lunches', 'Private minibus, Private vehicle, Taxi, Bike', 'Hotel (3 nights)', '- Hue - Imperial Citadel\r\n- Hue - Perfume River boat ride\r\n- Hue - Royal tomb of Emperor Tu Duc', '', 1, 'VCHC - HUE\'S SERENITY UNVEILED', 'Experience the charm of Hue in this central Vietnam tour by joining a city tour, cycling to Pha Tam Giang and taking a trip to the local Thuy Lap craft villag