(23, 'VHMC -  FROM SOUTHERN VIETNAM TO CAMBODIA', 'An interesting journey from vibrant Ho chi Minh city and tranquil Mekong Delta to Phnom Penh capital and magnificent Angkor Wat will leave you unforgettable moments in lifetime.', '', '', '<h2 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\">An remarkable journey from Southern Vietnam to Cambodia&nbsp;</span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">An interesting trip from Southern Vietnam to Cambodia by speedboat will leave you unforgettable moments. You will start exploring historical sites in the bustle and hustle Ho Chi Minh then take a boat trip along Mekong river and through mazes of canals to feel the vibrant atmosphere at the floating market and local&rsquo;s life. Then spend couple days discover Phnom Penh capital with classic Khmer-style buildings, French architecture and Buddhist temples and Siem Reap - home to renowned Angkor Wat the largest religious monument of the world.</span></p>\r\n', '<h3 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">1. Please provide your full name exactly as per passport at the time of booking (including any middle names listed on your passport) for flight tickets.<br />\r\n2. A single supplement is available on this trip, subject to availability. Please contact your sales agent if you would like to book this.&nbsp;<br />\r\n3. This trip includes a domestic flight. Checked luggage allowance is a maximum 20kg, with up to 7kg carry on luggage. Any excess luggage charges will need to be paid directly to the airline at check-in.<br />\r\n4. An airport arrival transfer is included. Please provide your flight details at the time of booking.</span><br />\r\n&nbsp;</h3>\r\n', '', 1328, 0, 0, 'FROM-SOUTHERN-VIETNAM-TO-CAMBODIA-9-days-8-nights-Greentours-Indochina.jpg', '[\"{\\\"image\\\":\\\"VHMC-Cambodia-Greentours-Indochina.jpg\\\"}\",\"{\\\"image\\\":\\\"VHMC-Sai-Gon-Greentours-Indochina.jpg\\\"}\"]', '2019-10-29 11:10:11', '