(24, 'VNS - SAPA TREKKING ADVENTURE', 'Get overwhelmed by Sapa landscapes, which are intertwined with human creativity, the topography of the mountains and lushful forest, filling the land with dreamy colors. Sapa is a land of tranquility that is the home of many natural wonders.', '', '', '<h2 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\">Sapa - The prosperous land of natural wonders</span></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Located in the northwestern Vietnam, Sapa is a land of tranquility that is the home of&nbsp;many natural wonders. The landscape of Sapa is intertwined with human creativity, the topography of the mountains and the lushful&nbsp;forest, filling&nbsp;the land with dreamy colors. Coming to Sapa, you can trek the mountain trails to ethnic minorities&#39; villages&nbsp;Ta Van and Lao Chai, which possess the mysterious and wild natural scenery that can captivate any traveller. Trek to Giang Ta Chai, the home to the Red Dzao minority group with colorful and traditional costume, through the vast rice fields, poetic bamboo forest and stunning waterfalls. Take a walk&nbsp;around Sapa to attractions such as the Cathedral or ethnic market for some local goods and take in the peaceful sight of the local lifestyle.</span></p>\r\n', '<h3 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">1. Please provide your full name exactly as per passport at the time of booking (including any middle names listed on your passport).&nbsp;<br />\r\n2. A single supplement is available on this trip, subject to availability. Please contact your sales agent if you would like to book this.&nbsp;</span></h3>\r\n', '', 148, 0, 0, 'Sapa-trekking-adventure-Greentours-Indochina.jpg', '[\"{\\\"image\\\":\\\"GRAND-VIETNAM-EXPLORATION-Greentours-Indochina.jpg\\\"}\",\"{\\\"image\\\":\\\"NORTHERN-VIETNAM-Greentours-Indochina.jpg\\\"}\"]', '2019-10-31 08:10:34', '2019-12-26 09:12:39', 0, 0, 