(25, 'LNH - HIGHLIGHTS OF LAOS', 'From Luang Prabang with its inherent ancient beauty to the tranquil city of Vientiane, you can enjoy a high-class life and indulge in the nature of Laos. Come to Laos to admire the timeless cutural and historical features of this strikingly peaceful country!', '', '', '<h2 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\">Discover Laos from Vientiane to Luang Prabang</span></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Laos, the country known as &quot;the land of millions of elephants&quot; embraces in itself plenty of secrets that enrapture many travellers. From Luang Prabang with its inherent ancient beauty to the tranquil city of Vientiane, you can enjoy a high-class life and relax after a busy day as well as explore the peaceful landscapes and indulge yourself in nature. Come to Laos to admire the&nbsp;timeless cutural and historical features of this strikingly&nbsp;peaceful country!</span></p>\r\n', '<h3 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">1. Please provide your full name exactly as per passport at the time of booking (including any middle names listed on your passport).&nbsp;<br />\r\n2. A single supplement is available on this trip, subject to availability. Please contact your sales agent if you would like to book this.&nbsp;</span></h3>\r\n', '', 1280, 0, 0, 'HIGHLIGHTS-OF-LAOS-Greentours-Indochina.jpg', '[\"{\\\"image\\\":\\\"VIETNAM-LAOS-AT-A-GLANCE-Greentours-Indochina.jpg\\\"}\",\"{\\\"image\\\":\\\"ESSENCE-OF-LAOS-Greentours-Indochina.jpg\\\"}\"]', '2019-10-31 09:10:11', '2019-12-26 10:12:08', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '', '', '[]', '', '', '', '', '', '7 breakfasts, 6 lunches', 'Boat, Private vehicle, Taxi', 'Hotel (7 nights)', '- Vientiane - Wat Haw Phra Kaew, Wat Si Saket, Pratu Xai, Pha That Luang\r\n- Vang Vieng - Tubing adventure and cave exploring\r\n- Luang Prabang - Kuang Si Waterfalls\r\n- Luang Prabang - Pak Ou Caves - Cr