(26, 'LSP - PANORAMIC SOUTHERN LAOS', 'Go on an adventure to discover the new routes, visit Laos plateau with lush coffee plantation, admire the dolphins on the Mekong River and peek in to the great culture through the unique temples of Laos.', '', '', '<h2><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\">Adventure in the&nbsp;central area of southern Laos</span></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">You will go on an adventure to discover the new routes, visit Laos plateau with lush coffee plantation, admire the dolphins on the Mekong River and peek in to the great culture through the unique temples. Explore Bolaven Plateau - the home to a number of tribal villages. Visit Tad Fane and Tad Lo waterfalls, a tea and coffee plantation. These beautiful attractions are the primary tourist destinations for further adventures into this remote province. The waterfall offers a relaxing environment and a range of guest houses and resorts styled in traditional architecture. Trek&nbsp;deep into the Xe Pian tropical forest and to Phou Asa archaeological site for a paranomic view.&nbsp;Hop on a cruise passing by the largest waterfalls in Asia in Don Khong to admire the majestic beauty of nature.</span></p>\r\n', '<h3 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">1. Please provide your full name exactly as per passport at the time of booking (including any middle names listed on your passport).&nbsp;<br />\r\n2. A single supplement is available on this trip, subject to availability. Please contact your sales agent if you would like to book this.&nbsp;</span></h3>\r\n', '', 960, 0, 0, 'PANORAMIC-SOUTHERN-LAOS-Greentours-Indochina.jpg', '[\"{\\\"image\\\":\\\"PLAIN-OF-JARS-IN-PHONSAVAN-Greentours-Indochina.jpg\\\"}\",\"{\\\"image\\\":\\\"HIGHLIGHTS-OF-LAOS-Greentours-Indochina.jpg\\\"}\"]', '2019-10-31 10:10:16', '2019-12-26 10:12:58', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '', '', '[]', '', '', '', '', '', '5 breakfasts, 4 lunches, 3 dinners', 'Boat, Private vehicle', 'Hotel (4 nights)\r\nCampsite (1 night)', '- Bolaven Plateau - Visit Tad Fane and Tad Lo waterfalls\r\n- Bolaven Plateau - Xe Pian tropical forest and to Phou Asa archaeological site trekking\r\n- Don Khong Island - Visit Khone Phapheng and Li Phi Falls', '', 1, 'LSP - PANORAMIC SOUTHERN LAOS', 'Go on an adventure to discover the new routes, visit Laos plateau with lush coffee plantation, admire the dolphins on the Mekong River and peek in to the great culture through the unique temples of Laos.', 'lsp-panoramic-southern-laos', 'southern Laos, Laos tour, Indochina tour, Greentours', NULL, '', '', '', NULL, NULL, '154,145,145', 0, 0, '', 'Pakse', 'Pakse', 'Laos', '', 'Adventure', 'LSP', '4', '', '', 'LSP-Greentours-Indochina-442x622.png', 'Ongtue-Temple-Laos-Greentours-Indochina.jpg', 'Ongtue Temple, Laos'),
(27, 'LNJ - PLAIN OF JARS IN PHONSAVAN', 'Visit the Plain of Jars, a megalithic archaeological landscape in Laos, which was created by Mon-Khmer group whose culture remains a mystery of humanity  to this day.', '', '', '<h2 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\">Explore Phonsavan - The Plain of Jars</span></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Come and visit the Plain of Jars, a famous archaeological site in Phonsavan. The Plain of Jars is a megalithic archaeological landscape in Laos. It consists of thousands of stone jars scattered along the valley and central plains of Xieng Khuoang Plateau. Archaeologists believe that the jars in this field date back 1500 to 2000 years, created by people of the Mon-Khmer group. Mon-Khmer culture to this day remains a mystery of humanity.</span></p>\r\n', '<h3 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">1. Please provide your full name exactly as per passport at the time of booking (including any middle names listed on your passport).&nbsp;<br />\r\n2. A single supplement is available on this trip, subject to availability. Please contact your sales agent if you would like to book this.&nbsp;</span></h3>\r\n', '', 480, 0, 0, 'PLAIN-OF-JARS-IN-PHONSAVAN-Greentours-Indochina.jpg', '[\"{\\\"image\\\":\\\"HIGHLIGHTS-OF-LAOS-Greentours-Indochina.jpg\\\"}\",\"{\\\"image\\\":\\\"ESSENCE-OF-LAOS-Greentours-Indochina.jpg\\\"}\"]', '2019-10-31 10:10:08', '2019-12-26 10:12:46', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '', '', '[]', '', '', '', '', '', '2 breakfasts, 1 lunche, 1 dinner', 'Private vehicle', 'Hotel (2 nights)', '- Xieng Khouang - Visit Buddhist sites, historic temples and caves\r\n- Phonsavan - Visit Plain of Jars, a megalithic archaeological landscape', '', 1, 'LNJ - PLAIN OF JARS IN PHONSAVAN', 'Visit the Plain of Jars, a megalithic archaeological landscape in Laos, which was created by Mon-Khmer group whose culture remains a mystery of humanity  to this day.', 'lnj-plain-of-jars-in-phonsavan', 'Plain of Jars tour, Laos tour, Indochina tour, Greentours', NULL, '', '', '', NULL, NULL, '148,145,145', 0, 0, '', 'Phonsavan', 'Phonsavan', 'Laos', '', 'Classic', 'LNJ', '2', '', '', 'LNJ-Greentours-Indochina-442x622.png', 'Laos-Monks-Greentours-Indochina.jpg', 'Laos'),
(28, 'VLS - VIETNAM & LAOS AT A GLANCE', 'A travel itinerary to destinations that are not new but still unique to discover Laos, the country of millions of elephants and Vietnam, the land of heritages.', '', '', '<h2 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\">One&nbsp;travel itinerary to discover two country - Laos&nbsp;and Vietnam</span></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">A travel itinerary to destinations that are not new but still unique to discover the country of millions of elephants&nbsp;- Laos&nbsp;and the land of heritages - Vietnam. Come to Vietnam, the&nbsp;dream destination&nbsp;with beautiful natural scenery, a long history, rich culture and unique cuisine, which will awaken&nbsp;all the senses of visitors. Explore Laos, a country of temples and festivals. The beautiful country of Laos owns many famous landscapes, pristine mountains and peaceful countryside. The ancient and unique architecture of pagodas can be found throughout Laos, such as&nbsp;majestic That&nbsp;Luang tower, Sisaket pagoda and&nbsp;Ho Phrakeo pagoda&nbsp;in the heart of Vientiane or&nbsp;Wat Xieng Thong and Wat Mai in Luang Prabang.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<h3 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">1. Please provide your full name exactly as per passport at the time of booking (including any middle names listed on your passport).&nbsp;<br />\r\n2. A single supplement is available on this trip, subject to availability. Please contact your sales agent if you would like to book this.&nbsp;</span></h3>\r\n', '', 1623, 0, 0, 'VIETNAM-LAOS-AT-A-GLANCE-Greentours-Indochina.jpg', '[\"{\\\"image\\\":\\\"ESSENCE-OF-LAOS-Greentours-Indochina.jpg\\\"}\",\"{\\\"image\\\":\\\"VLS-Laos-Greentours-Indochina.jpg\\\"}\"]', '2019-10-31 13:10:28', '2019-12-26 10:12:22', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '', '', '[]', '', '', '', '', '', '10 breakfasts, 4 lunches', 'Private vehicle, bus, taxi', 'Hotel (10 nights)', '- Full-day Ho Chi Minh city tour\r\n- Cruising along the Mekong River\r\n- Half-day city tour in Hoi An\r\n- Half-day city tour in Hue\r\n- Half-day city tour in Hanoi\r\n- Board the cruise through Halong Bay\r\n- Join the city tour around the former capital of Luang Prabang\r\n- Take a short tour around Siem Reap', '', 1, 'VLS - VIETNAM & LAOS AT A GLANCE', 'An exciting travel itinerary to destinations that are not new but still unique to discover Laos, the country of millions of elephants and Vietnam, the land of heritages.', 'vls-vietnam-laos-at-a-glance', 'Vietnam tour, Laos tour, Indochina tour, Greentours', NULL, '', '', '', NULL, NULL, '148,145,144,144', 0, 0, '', 'Ho Chi Minh', 'Vientiane', 'Vietnam, Laos', '', 'Classic', 'VLS', '2', '', '', 'VLP-S-Greentours-Indochina-442x622.png', 'VLS-Laos-tours-Greentours-Indochina.jpg', 'The landscape of Laos'),
