(40, ' VFH - FASCINATING VIETNAM FAMILY HOLIDAY', 'Endowed with numerous breathtaking natural landscapes, grandiose mountains and highlands as well as crystal blue beaches, Vietnam promises to be a wonderful destination for your family’s holiday.', '', '', '<h2><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\">Enjoy breathtaking landscapes and meet warm people in Vietnam&nbsp;</span></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Endowed with numerous breathtaking natural landscapes, grandiose highlands and mountains, crystal emerald beaches, Vietnam is a promising destination for your family&rsquo;s holiday. &nbsp;With this tour, you will go through most must-see attractions across the country, which give you chance to see historical sites with thousands of preserved&nbsp;relics and antiques, learn about rich culture and local&rsquo;s life, enjoy cruise trip at one of the Wonders of the Word, taste quintessential cuisine of the country and emerge yourself in beautiful sandy long beaches. A lot of fun activities and distinctive experience in each region will satisfy your children&rsquo;s curiosity.</span></p>\r\n', '<h3 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">1. Please provide your full name exactly as per passport at the time of booking (including any middle names listed on your passport) for flight tickets.<br />\r\n2. A single supplement is available on this trip, subject to availability. Please contact your sales agent if you would like to book this.&nbsp;<br />\r\n3. This trip includes a domestic flight. Checked luggage allowance is a maximum 20kg, with up to 7kg carry on luggage. Any excess luggage charges will need to be paid directly to the airline at check-in.<br />\r\n4. An airport arrival transfer is included. Please provide your flight details at the time of booking.</span><br />\r\n&nbsp;</h3>\r\n', '', 1142, 0, 0, 'Fascinating-Vietnam-Family-Holiday-13-days-12-nights-Greentours-Indochina