(52, 'VSC -  FLAVOURS OF SOUTHERN VIETNAM', '', '', '', '<h2><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\">Savour diversity of superb&nbsp;Southern Cuisine</span></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">This trip is well designed for you to experience and learn about Southern cuisine as well as visit popular sites in the region. Start the tour in Saigon where you will join a cooking class with local professional and enjoy various street foods then spend couple days in rustic Mekong delta, take a boat trip to visit floating market and try local specialties especially Hu Tieu which made the world renowned chef Gordon Ramsay be enamored of.</span></p>\r\n', '<h3 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">1. Please provide your full name exactly as per passport at the time of booking (including any middle names listed on your passport).&nbsp;Please check your booking information exactly matches your passport<br />\r\n2. A single supplement is available on this trip, subject to availability. Please contact your sales agent if you would like to book this.&nbsp;</span></h3>\r\n', '', 213, 10, 0, 'FLAVOURS-OF-SOUTHERN-VIETNAM-3-days-2-nights-Greentours-Indochina.jpg', '[\"{\\\"image\\\":\\\"VSC-Floating-Market-Mekong-Delta-Greentours-Indochina.jpg\\\"}\",\"{\\\"image\\\":\\\"VSC-Spring-Rolls-Greentours-Indochina.jpg\\\"}\"]', '2019-11-06 13:11:56', '2020-01-10 15:01:16', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '', '', '[]', '', '', '', '', '', '2 breakfasts, 3 lunches and 1 dinner', 'Private car, bus, boat', 'Hotel (2 nights)', 'Ho Chi Minh city - Cooking class, city tour\r\nMekong Delta - boat trip, cooking class, floating market', '', 1, 'VSC -  FLAVOURS OF SOUTHERN VIETNAM', 'This trip is well designed for you to learn about Southern cuisine. You will have chance to join cooking classes and enjoy various street foods with local guide', 'vsc-flavours-of-southern-vietnam', 'Southern Vietnam\'s cuisine', NULL, '', '', '', NUL