(140, 'Laos Golf', '<p>Being an experienced professional tour operator, we organize tours throughout Vietnam, Laos and Cambodia, ranging from classic tours to tailor-made themed tours such as cycling, kayaking or hiking and trekking tours.&nbsp;One of our strong points is organizing golf tours with special services for customers</p>\r\n', '<table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p style=\"text-align:center\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"554\" src=\"/image/images/Greentours%20charity%205.jpg\" width=\"738\" /></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<h1><strong>GREENTOURS supported members of the Blind Association in Thanh Mien, Hai Duong for Tet Holiday</strong></h1>\r\n\r\n			<p>On January 16, 2019, Greentours cooperated with Thai Nguyen Provincial People&#39;s Committee, Dong Hy District People&#39;s Committee and Tan Loi Commune People&#39;s Committee to present gifts for Tet Holiday to poor households in Tan Loi commune.&nbsp;Shortly after the ceremony was held at the headquarters of the People&#39;s Committee of Tan Loi Commune, despite the cold weather and rugged roads, the Board of Directors of Greentours came to Cau Luu hamlet to deliver the gifts of VND 50,000,000 in cash for Ms. Vuong Thi Phuong&#39;s family, with the desire to bring them a new and stable home to welcome a warm and happy Tet Holiday as well as some gifts for Tet Holiday to other households in Tan Loi commune.</p>\r\n\r\n			<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n			<p>These gifts however small, they carried in themselves a great meaning, which were the wishes of Greentours staff to people of Tan Loi commune, hoping that the unfortunate households would be able to welcome a warm, healthy and joyful Tet Holiday. <a href=\"https://greentoursindochina.com/greentours-presented-gifts-for-poor-households-in-tan-loi-commune\">See more</a></p>\r\n\r\n			<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<h1>&nbsp;</h1>\r\n\r\n			<h1><strong>GREENTOURS supported members of the Blind Association in Thanh Mien, Hai Duong for Tet Holiday</strong></h1>\r\n\r\n			<p>On January 28, 2019, the Board of Directors of Greentours JSC arrived in Thanh Mien district, Hai Duong province to present gifts for Tet Holiday to the member of the Blind Association who had a hard time making a living. Greentours presented a gift of VND 20,000,000 to the Blind Association in Thanh Mien District. This is a meaningful activity with the spirit of &ldquo;All for one, and one for all&quot; to encourage those who have unfortunate circumstances and help them overcome difficulties.</p>\r\n\r\n			<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n			<p>Though what Greentours had to offer was very small in comparison to the difficulties these people had to face, Greentours sincerely hoped that our effort would support the members to reduce the inferiority complex and build up self-esteem for them to celebrate a happy Lunar New Year with the community and society. <a href=\"https://greentoursindochina.com/greentours-supported-member-of-the-blind-association-in-thanh-mien-hai-duong-for-tet-holiday\">See more</a></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td><img alt=\"\" height=\"1200\" src=\"/image/images/Greentours%20charity%201.jpg\" width=\"1600\" /></td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', 146, 0, NULL, '2019-11-27 16:11:47', NULL, '', '', '', '', '', 1, 'Laos Golf', '', 'laos-golf', '', 1, 3),
