(143, 'Cambodia Tours', '<h2 style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-size:48px\">A lifetime experience&nbsp;in Kingdom of Wonders&nbsp;</span></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Cambodia is charming country in the Southeast Asia and a worth visiting place for its&nbsp;mysterious beauty, unique history and friendly people. Despite of tumultuous history, Cambodia has moved on and proved itself as one of the hottest tourist destinations in the region. It cannot be denied that magnificent and impressive Angkor Wat - the largest religious monument in the world has made Cambodia well - known to the world, but it is not the only great thing to discover about the country. Besides ancient temples, Cambodia offers travelers natural sights of waterfalls, untouched islands, pretty beaches, jungles, cafe-culture in lively cities as well as peaceful countryside landscapes. Let&rsquo;s explore any of our itineraries to have an interesting and memorable trip!</span></p>\r\n', '<table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"5\" cellspacing=\"0\">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><strong><img alt=\"\" height=\"435\" src=\"/image/images/Responsible%201.jpg\" width=\"580\" /></strong>\r\n			<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<h3 style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-size:22px\"><strong>BUILDING HOUSES &amp; SUPPLYING WORK TOOLS</strong></span></span></h3>\r\n\r\n			<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Family in rural area in need to build a house, We create project by project to locate the families in need to have houses which help them to have the first step in stabilizing their lives. We have launched in projects to built houses for poor farmers in Hai Duong and Thai Nguyen provinces. The projects will extend to other provinces of Cao Băng, Son La of Vietnam. The next step of the project is to supply work tools for poor farmers. The most valuable work tools are giving cows (For ploughing in paddy field) where the field is terrace so no plough machine can help. <a href=\"https://greentoursindochina.com/greentours-presented-gifts-for-poor-households-in-tan-loi-commune\">See more</a>.</span></p>\r\n\r\n			<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<h3 style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-size:22px\"><strong>BRING CHILDREN TO SCHOOLS</strong></span></span></h3>\r\n\r\n			<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">We&rsquo;re not trying to give candy, pens, notepads, sweets, chocolates, money, or any other gifts to&nbsp;<em>random kids on the street. It</em>&nbsp;is a horrible idea. <strong><em>If you want to give to the kids, by all means, do so!</em>&nbsp;</strong>Donate to a local church, mosque, school, or charity. Give school supplies or soccer balls or toys, but give them to adults to distribute.</span></p>\r\n\r\n			<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Green Tours Indochina has worked with local authorities in rural areas in&nbsp;the North of Vietnam to supply needs for children including: Backpack and other book bags, Calculators, Spiral bound composition and other notebooks, Filler paper, Colored pencils, crayons and markers, Ruler with English and metric measurements, Colored pens, Erasers...</span></p>\r\n\r\n			<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">The project extends to build class rooms in remote areas. Please contact us on the occasions if you can help by&nbsp;your particular work based on your skills from simple work like carrying brinks, hanging pictures to making&nbsp;a drawing for the whole class room.</span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td><img alt=\"\" height=\"649\" src=\"/image/images/Responsible%202.jpg\" width=\"971\" /></td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 141, 0, 'cambodia.jpg', '2019-12-21 18:12:01', NULL, 'Cambodia Tours & Travel info', '<iframe width=\"1110\" height=\"642\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/boe7b80IKvA\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen></iframe>', '', '', '', 1, 'Cambodia Tours', 'Cambodia is a charming country in Southeast Asia and a worth visiting place for its mysterious beauty, unique history and friendly people. Cambodia offers travelers natural sights of waterfalls, untouched islands and beaches, jungles as well as peaceful countryside landscapes.', 'cambodia-tours', 'Cambodia tour, Cambodia Golf package, Indochina tour, Greentours', 1, 1),
(144, 'Vietnam Tours', '<h2 style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:48px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">A burst of flavour</span></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Wherever you go, the tastes of the local culinary are what will keep lingering in your memory and urging you to come back. Hardly anywhere can you find a place filled with mouth-watering delicacies with rich flavours as in Vietnam, be it at an extravagant restaurant downtown or a small savoury food-stall at the side of the street. You can slurp away your bowl of hot &#39;pho&#39; in the freezing winter and enjoy the warm sensation running through your veins; savour Hue lotus seed sweet soup to be engulfed in the light sweetness intermixing with the faint fragrance of lotus; take a mouthful of the crispy &#39;banh xeo&#39; (rice crepe) levelled up by the fresh herbs and vegetables; or just simply sit by the road and sip on a creamy egg coffee while gazing at the bustling local life.</span></p>\r\n', '<table border=\"1\" bordercolor=\"#ccc\" cellpadding=\"5\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse:collapse\">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><img alt=\"\" height=\"435\" src=\"/image/images/Responsible%201.jpg\" width=\"580\" />\r\n			<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<h3 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-size:22px\"><strong>BUILDING HOUSES AND SUPPLYING WORK TOOLS</strong></span></span></h3>\r\n\r\n			<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Family in rural area in need to build a house, We create project by project to locate the families in need to have houses which help them to have the first step in stabilizing their lives. We have launched in projects to built houses for poor farmers in Hai Duong and Thai Nguyen provinces. The projects will extend to other provinces of Cao Bang, Son La of Vietnam. The next step of the project is to supply work tools for poor farmers. The most valuable work tools are giving cows (For ploughing in paddy field) where the field is terrace so no plough machine can help. <strong><a href=\"https://greentoursindochina.com/greentours-presented-gifts-for-poor-households-in-tan-loi-commune\"><span style=\"color:#e74c3c\">See more</span></a><span style=\"color:#e74c3c\">.</span></strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n			<p style=\"text-align:center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<h3 style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:22px\"><strong><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"color:black\">BRING CHILDREN TO SCHOOLS</span></span></strong></span></h3>\r\n\r\n			<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"color:black\">We&rsquo;re not trying to give candy, pens, notepads, sweets, chocolates, money, or any other gifts to&nbsp;<em>random kids on the street. It</em>&nbsp;is a horrible idea. </span></span><strong><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"color:black\"><em>If you want to give to the kids, by all means, do so!</em>&nbsp;</span></span></strong><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"color:black\">Donate to a local church, mosque, school, or charity. Give school supplies or soccer balls or toys, but give them to adults to distribute.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n			<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"color:black\">Green Tours Indochina has worked with local authorities in rural areas in&nbsp;the North of Vietnam to supply needs for children including: </span></span>Backpack and other book bags, Calculators, Spiral bound composition and other notebooks, Filler paper, Colored pencils, crayons and markers, Ruler with English and metric measurements, Colored pens, Erasers...</span></p>\r\n\r\n			<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"color:black\">The project extends to build class rooms in remote areas. Please contact us on the occasions if you can help by&nbsp;your particular work based on your skills from simple work like carrying brinks, hanging pictures to making&nbsp;a drawing for the whole class room.</span></span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td><img alt=\"\" height=\"649\" src=\"/image/images/Responsible%202.jpg\" width=\"971\" /></td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', 141, 0, 'vietnam.jpg', '2019-12-21 18:12:24', NULL, 'Vietnam Tours & Travel info', '<iframe width=\"1110\" height=\"642\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/ljuZFbn4nU4\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen></iframe>', '', '', '', 1, 'Vietnam Tours', 'Greentours Indochina organnizes tours through-out Vietnam from classic tours to active tours, Vietnam family packages, culinary tours to cruising trips. Golf tour is one of our service highlights which is specially designed for each guest to conquer the most challenging golf courses in Vietnam.', 'vietnam-tours', 'highlight of Vietnam tour, from north to the south of Vietnam tour, from the south to the north Vietnam tours, throughout Vietnam tours, Vietnam bycle tours, Vietnam family tours, Vietnam active tours, Vietnam cruising tours, Vietnam classic tours, Vietnam culinary tours.', 1, 1),
(145, 'Laos Tours', '<h2 style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-size:48px\">Tranquility in simplicity</span></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Laos, an agricultural country specialised in rice farming, possesses a myriad of magnificent mountains, vast untouched forests, countless rice paddy fields and endlessly expanded river, which brings about infinite tourism potential for this land. Laotian culture is the combination of several other cultures including Thailand and China and also embraces the diversity of many different ethnic minority groups living in the country. Likewise, food is an important part that Laotians take great pride in sharing with foreign travellers, which should be more widely known to the world. The unique laidback local life said to be unchanged for years and decades creates a tranquil and peaceful atmosphere that is hard to find anywhere else. Away from the bustling urban lifestyles, this is where your souls will be nurtured and rejuvenated.</span></p>\r\n', '<table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"5\" cellspacing=\"0\">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td><strong><span style=\"font-size:22px\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"435\" src=\"/image/images/Responsible%201.jpg\" width=\"580\" /></span></strong></td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<h3><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:22px\">BUILDING HOUSES AND SUPPLYING WORK TOOLS</span></strong></span></h3>\r\n\r\n			<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">For family in rural area in need to build a house, we create project by project to&nbsp;help them during&nbsp;their&nbsp;first step in stabilizing their lives. We have launched in projects to built houses for poor farmers in Hai Duong and Thai Nguyen provinces. The projects will extend to other provinces of Cao Băng, Son La of Vietnam. The next step of the project is to supply work tools for poor farmers. The most valuable work tools are giving cows (For ploughing in paddy field) where the field is terrace so no plough machine can help. <a href=\"https://greentoursindochina.com/greentours-presented-gifts-for-poor-households-in-tan-loi-commune\">See more</a>.</span></p>\r\n\r\n			<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<h3><span style=\"color:#000000\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:22px\">BRING CHILDREN TO SCHOOLS</span></strong></span></h3>\r\n\r\n			<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">We&rsquo;re not trying to give candy, pens, notepads, sweets, chocolates, money, or any other gifts to&nbsp;<em>random kids on the street. It</em>&nbsp;is a horrible idea. <strong><em>If you want to give them to the kids, by all means, do so!</em>&nbsp;</strong>Donate to a local church, mosque, school, or charity. Give school supplies, soccer balls or toys, but give them to adults to distribute.</span></p>\r\n\r\n			<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Greentours Indochina has worked with local authorities in rural areas in&nbsp;the North of Vietnam to supply needs for children including: Backpack and other book bags, Calculators, Spiral bound composition and other notebooks, Filler paper, Colored pencils, crayons and markers, Ruler with English and metric measurements, Colored pens, Erasers...</span></p>\r\n\r\n			<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">The project extends to build class rooms in remote areas. Please contact us on the occasions if you can help by&nbsp;your particular work based on your skills from simple work like carrying brinks, hanging pictures to making&nbsp;a drawing for the whole class room.</span></p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td><img alt=\"\" height=\"649\" src=\"/image/images/Responsible%202.jpg\" width=\"971\" /></td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n', 141, 0, 'laos.jpg', '2019-12-21 18:12:42', NULL, 'Laos Tours & Travel info', '<iframe width=\"1110\" height=\"642\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/f3jHlOXhn-E\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen></iframe>', '', '', '', 1, 'Laos Tours', 'Laos, an agricultural country specialised in rice farming, possesses a myriad of magnificent mountains, vast untouched forests, countless rice paddy fields and endlessly expanded river, which brings about infinite tourism potential for this land. ', 'laos-tours', 'Laos tour', 1, 1),
