price before buying things except at fixed price stores.</span></p>\r\n', 147, 0, 'Family-packages-Greentours-Indochina-1.jpg', '2020-01-10 15:01:27', NULL, '', '', '', '', '', 1, 'Family Packages', 'Admire the beautiful scenery, the green primeval forests and go on an exciting adventure of your own. Participate in kayaking, cycling, hiking or interacting with the indigenous people. The simplicity and hospitality that can be found anywhere in Indochina will make you eager to return for more. ', 'family-packages', 'Vietnam tour, Laos tour, Cambodia tour, Indochina tour, Greentours, Family Packages', NULL, 2),
(151, 'Culinary Tours', '<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:48px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">Indochina within your reach</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Pull yourself away from the bustling daily life to seek for self-relaxation and let your mind wander with the clouds, to think less and feel more. Admire the beautiful scenery, the green primeval forests and go on an exciting adventure of your own. Participate in kayaking, cycling, hiking or interacting with the indigenous people. The simplicity, friendliness and hospitality that can be found anywhere in Indochina will make you eager to return for more.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n', '<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><strong>1.&nbsp;Food list</strong>:&nbsp;While you explore new cuisines, take a list of dishes and food spots to make sure that you don&rsquo;t miss any famous local specialty.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><strong>2. Small first-aid kit</strong>: Keeping digestive pills and common&nbsp;medicines with you is essential to stay healthy during the trip because trying the local food and new flavors can be quite upsetting for the stomach.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><strong>3. Respect culture</strong>: A culinary trip is not just about enjoying foods, it also a chance to visit local attractions; so keep in mind to dress appropriately and take your footwear off when visiting local religious sites or temples.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><strong>4. Watch belongings</strong>: In general, Indochina is a safe place for travelling, but you should keep an eye on your valuables in crowded places or markets&nbsp;to avoid petty theft.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><strong>5. Shop</strong>: Negotiate&nbsp;the price before buying things except at fixed price stores.</span></p>\r\n', 147, 0, 'Culinary-Green-tours-Indochina.jpg', '2020-01-10 15:01:43', NULL, '', '', '', '', '', 1, 'Culinary Tours', 'Admire the beautiful scenery, the green primeval forests and go on an exciting adventure of your own. Participate in kayaking, cycling, hiking or interacting with the indigenous people. The simplicity and hospitality that can be found anywhere in Indochina will make you eager to return for more. ', 'culinary-tours', 'Vietnam tour, Laos tour, Cambodia tour, Indochina tour, Greentours, Culinary Tours', NULL, 2),
(152, 'Urban Tours', '<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:48px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">Indochina within your reach</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Pull yourself away from the bustling daily life to seek for self-relaxation and let your mind wander with the clouds, to think less and feel more. Admire the beautiful scenery, the green primeval forests and go on an exciting adventure of your own. Participate in kayaking, cycling, hiking or interacting with the indigenous people. The simplicity, friendliness and hospitality that can be found anywhere in Indochina will make you eager to return for more.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n', '<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><strong>1. Things to pack:</strong> Wear sunscreen, hat, sunglasses, comfortable clothes and footwear for walking.<br />\r\n<strong>2. Respect culture</strong>: Dress modestly and appropriately and take off shoes at local religious sites.<br />\r\n<strong>3. Watch belongings</strong>: Indochina is a safe place for travelling but you should still keep an eye on your valuables in crowded places.<br />\r\n<strong>4. Good camera</strong>: Don&#39;t forget to prepare a good camera or phone with full battery to take perfect shots of places you visit.</span><br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 147, 0, 'Bicycle-and-street-vendor-Vietnam-Greentours-Indochina.jpg', '2020-01-10 15:01:31', NULL, '', '', '', '', '', 1, 'Urban Tours', 'Admire the beautiful scenery, the green primeval forests and go on an exciting adventure of your own. Participate in kayaking, cycling, hiking or interacting with the indigenous people. The simplicity and hospitality that can be found anywhere in Indochina will make you eager to return for more. ', 'urban-tours', 'Vietnam tour, Laos tour, Cambodia tour, Indochina tour, Greentours, Urban Tours', NULL, 2),
(154, 'Active Adventure', '<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-size:48px\">Indochina within your reach</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Pull yourself away from the bustling daily life to seek for self-relaxation and let your mind wander with the clouds, to think less and feel more. Admire the beautiful scenery, the green primeval forests and go on an exciting adventure of your own. Participate in kayaking, cycling, hiking or interacting with the indigenous people. The simplicity, friendliness and hospitality that can be found anywhere in Indochina will make you eager to return for more.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n', '<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">1. <strong>Pack light: </strong>Packing&nbsp;small is essential for any globetrotter committed to embracing the chaos of travel.&nbsp;Traveling light allows you to make better on-the-ground choices.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">2. <strong>Share your experience: </strong>Capture the essence of your experience and share it with others. Tell a story that inspires other people to travel and care about people and place.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">3. <strong>Be active: </strong>There is no better, or more sustainable&nbsp;way to experience a destination than through human-powered adventure. Build sweat equity with a destination and it forever becomes a part of you.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">4.&nbsp;<strong>Just go!</strong> There&rsquo;s always a reason to postpone. But don&rsquo;t do that. Book a trip and you won&rsquo;t regret it. Adventure travel can be very affordable, with extraordinary experiences available at every price point. Not going is the only thing you&rsquo;ll regret.</span></p>\r\n', 147, 0, 'adventure.jpg', '2019-12-21 16:12:42', NULL, '', '', '', '', '', 1, 'Active Adventure', 'Admire the beautiful scenery, the green primeval forests and go on an exciting adventure of your own. Participate in kayaking, cycling, hiking or interacting with the indigenous people. The simplicity and hospitality that can be found anywhere in Indochina will make you eager to return for more. ', 'active-adventure', 'Vietnam tour, Laos tour, Cambodia tour, Indochina tour, Greentours, Active Adventure', NULL, 2),
(155, 'Cruising', '<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-size:48px\">Indochina within your reach</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Pull yourself away from the bustling daily life to seek for self-relaxation and let your mind wander with the clouds, to think less and feel more. Admire the beautiful scenery, the green primeval forests and go on an exciting adventure of your own. Participate in kayaking, cycling, hiking or interacting with the indigenous people. The simplicity, friendliness and hospitality that can be found anywhere in Indochina will make you eager to return for more.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n', '<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><strong>1. Things to pack</strong>: Wear sunscreen and sunglasses&nbsp;to protect your skin from the sun, bring swimsuit if swimming and wear casual and comfortable clothes.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><strong>2.&nbsp;Best time to cruise</strong>: From October until January is the best time to take a boat trip in Indochina as it is just after the rainy season and the water level will be at their peak, however depending each region, you can visit in other time too.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><strong>3. Good camera:&nbsp;</strong>Don&#39;t forget to prepare a good camera or phone with full battery to take perfect shots of places you visit.</span><br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 147, 0, 'cruising.jpg', '2019-12-21 16:12:51', NULL, '', '', '', '', '', 1, 'Cruising', 'Admire the beautiful scenery, the green primeval forests and go on an exciting adventure of your own. Participate in kayaking, cycling, hiking or interacting with the indigenous people. The simplicity and hospitality that can be found anywhere in Indochina will make you eager to return for more. ', 'cruising', 'Vietnam tour, Laos tour, Cambodia tour, Indochina tour, Greentours, Cruising', NULL, 2),
