(277, 146, 'Golf', 'vn', '<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Our strong point is to organize golf tours with special services for customers including: Assisting golfers in registering for local&nbsp;tournaments. Golf experience exchange and business opportunity seeking with local merchants. Golf clubs for rent and golf tour combined&nbsp;with local cultural and culinary discovery. Please see in detail our services bellow.</span></p>\r\n', '', '', '', '', '', '', 0, 'golf-tours', 'Cambodia golf tour, Vietnam golf tour, Laos golf tour, Indochina golf tour', 'Golf Tours', 'Organize golf tours with special services for customers including: Assisting golfers in registering for local tournaments; Golf experience exchange and business opportunity seeking with local merchants; Golf clubs for rent and golf tour combined with local cultural and culinary discovery. '),
