(289, 152, 'Urban Tours', 'vn', '<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:48px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">Indochina within your reach</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Pull yourself away from the bustling daily life to seek for self-relaxation and let your mind wander with the clouds, to think less and feel more. Admire the beautiful scenery, the green primeval forests and go on an exciting adventure of your own. Participate in kayaking, cycling, hiking or interacting with the indigenous people. The simplicity, friendliness and hospitality that can be found anywhere in Indochina will make you eager to return for more.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n', '<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><strong>1. Things to pack:</strong> Wear sunscreen, hat, sunglasses, comfortable clothes and footwear for walking.<br />\r\n<strong>2. Respect culture</strong>: Dress modestly and appropriately and take off shoes at local religious sites.<br />\r\n<strong>3. Watch belongings</strong>: Indochina is a safe place for travelling but you should still keep an eye on your valuables in crowded places.<br />\r\n<strong>4. Good camera</strong>: Don&#39;t forget to prepare a good camera or phone with full battery to take perfect shots of places you visit.</span><br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '', '', '', '', '', 0, 'urban-tours', 'Vietnam tour, Laos tour, Cambodia tour, Indochina tour, Greentours, Urban Tours', 'Urban Tours', 'Admire the beautiful scenery, the green primeval forests and go on an exciting adventure of your own. Participate in kayaking, cycling, hiking or interacting with the indigenous people. The simplicity and hospitality that can be found anywhere in Indochina will make you eager to return for more. '),
