(27, 14, 'vn', 'LNS - ESSENCE OF LAOS', 'Laos embraces in itself plenty of secrets that enrapture many travellers. Enjoy a high-class life and relax after a busy day, or explore the peaceful landscapes and indulge yourself in nature with Laos tour from Greentours Indochina.', '', '', '<h2 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\">Discover Laos from Luang Prabang to Pakse</span></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Laos, the country known as &quot;the land of millions of elephants&quot; embraces in itself plenty of secrets that enrapture many travellers. From Luang Prabang with&nbsp;its inherent ancient beauty and&nbsp;famous archaeological site in Phonsavan, or the peaceful countryside with immense green forests and mountains - Vang Vieng - and the tranquil city of Vientiane to Pakse,&nbsp;the perfect central hub of southern Laos. You can enjoy a high-class life and relax after a busy day as well as&nbsp;explore the peaceful landscapes and indulge yourself in nature.</span></p>\r\n', '<h3 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">1. Please provide your full name exactly as per passport at the time of booking (including any middle names listed on your passport) for train and flight tickets.&nbsp;<br />\r\n2. A single supplement is available on this trip, subject to availability. Please contact your sales agent if you would like to book this.&nbsp;<br />\r\n3. This trip includes a domestic flight. Checked luggage allowance is a maximum 20kg, with up to 7kg carry on luggage. Any excess luggage charges will need to be paid directly to the airline at check-in.</span></h3>\r\n', '', '', '', '[]', '', '', '', '', '', '11 breakfasts, 7 lunches, 1 dinner', 'Boat, Plane, Private minibus, Private vehicle, Taxi', 'Hotel (11 nights)', '- Luang Prabang - Kuang Si Waterfalls \r\n- Luang Prabang - Pak Ou Caves \r\n- Phonsavan - Plain of Jars, a famous archaeological site\r