(29, 15, 'vn', 'VSG - SOUTHERN VIETNAM GOLF PACKAGE', '', '', '', '<h2><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">Enjoy&nbsp;excellent courses with scenic views in Southern&nbsp;Vietnam</span></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Vietnam is well known for its breathtaking nature from mountain to the sea and from the North to the South, so wherever you go, you can still play golf and enjoy distinctive charming landscape of that region. This 8 day tour is an ideal trip for you to start playing at the most excellent courses in bustling Ho Chi Minh city then visit temperate highland of Da Lat to play a round in the cool climate, fresh air with scenic views and last stop at Nha Trang - one of the most beautiful coastal cities in Vietnam where you can experience the world-class courses and relax at the luxury resorts.</span></p>\r\n', '<h3 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">1. Please provide your full name exactly as per passport at the time of booking (including any middle names listed on your passport).<br />\r\n2. A single supplement is available on this trip, subject to availability. Please contact your sales agent if you would like to book this.&nbsp;<br />\r\n3. An airport arrival transfer is included. Please provide your flight details at the time of booking.</span></h3>\r\n', '', '', '', '[]', '', '', '', '', '', '7 breakfasts and 1 lunch', 'Private vehicle, plane', 'Hotel (7 nights)', 'Ho Chi Minh - Vietnam Golf & Country Club and city tour\r\nHo Chi Minh - Song Be Golf Resort\r\nDalat - Dalat Palace Golf Club \r\nNha Trang - Diamond Bay Golf resort\r\nNha Trang -  Vinpearl Golf Club', '', 0, 'vsg-southern-vietnam-golf-package', 'VSG - SOUTHERN VIETNAM GOLF PACKAGE', 'Join with us to play some rounds at world-class courses and enjoy scenic charming landscapes in vibrant Ho Chi Minh, picturesque Dalat and beautiful coastal Nha Trang city', 'Southern Vietnam golf'),
