(43, 22, 'vn', 'VCHL - VIETNAM AND CAMBODIA HIGHLIGHTS', 'This combination trip brings you to most popular destinations in Vietnam and Cambodia to discover unique culture and heritage, spectacular landscapes and meet warm local of 2 countries.', '', '', '<h2><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\">Explore highlights of Vietnam and Cambodia</span></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">This combination trip brings you through most of &nbsp;the popular destinations of 2 neighbouring countries. From Hanoi - the thousand-year-old capital city to breathtaking Ha Long bay,&nbsp;down to charming central region to lively Sai Gon, then to bustling capital of Phnom Penh and last stop at majestic temple of Angkor Wat - the largest religious monument in the world. This is definitely a memorable vacation in your traveling life.</span></p>\r\n', '<h3 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">1. Please provide your full name exactly as per passport at the time of booking (including any middle names listed on your passport) for flight tickets.<br />\r\n2. A single supplement is available on this trip, subject to availability. Please contact your sales agent if you would like to book this.&nbsp;<br />\r\n3. This trip includes a domestic flight. Checked luggage allowance is a maximum 20kg, with up to 7kg carry on luggage. Any excess luggage charges will need to be paid directly to the airline at check-in.<br />\r\n4. An airport arrival transfer is included. Please provide your flight details at the time of booking.</span><br />\r\n&nbsp;</h3>\r\n', '', '', '', '[]', '', '', '', '', '', '15 breakfasts, 7 lunches and 1 dinner', 'Private vehicles, airplane, bus, bike, boat, cruise.', 'Hotel ( 15 nights)', 'Hanoi - City tour\r\nHa Long Bay - Cruising, kayaking\r\nHue - Sightseeing\r\nHoi An - Farming and Fishing Life Tour\r\nHo Chi Minh -  Visit city\'s highlights\r\nMekong Delta - Boat trip \r\nPhnom Penh 