(51, 26, 'vn', 'LSP - PANORAMIC SOUTHERN LAOS', 'Go on an adventure to discover the new routes, visit Laos plateau with lush coffee plantation, admire the dolphins on the Mekong River and peek in to the great culture through the unique temples of Laos.', '', '', '<h2><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\">Adventure in the&nbsp;central area of southern Laos</span></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">You will go on an adventure to discover the new routes, visit Laos plateau with lush coffee plantation, admire the dolphins on the Mekong River and peek in to the great culture through the unique temples. Explore Bolaven Plateau - the home to a number of tribal villages. Visit Tad Fane and Tad Lo waterfalls, a tea and coffee plantation. These beautiful attractions are the primary tourist destinations for further adventures into this remote province. The waterfall offers a relaxing environment and a range of guest houses and resorts styled in traditional architecture. Trek&nbsp;deep into the Xe Pian tropical forest and to Phou Asa archaeological site for a paranomic view.&nbsp;Hop on a cruise passing by the largest waterfalls in Asia in Don Khong to admire the majestic beauty of nature.</span></p>\r\n', '<h3 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">1. Please provide your full name exactly as per passport at the time of booking (including any middle names listed on your passport).&nbsp;<br />\r\n2. A single supplement is available on this trip, subject to availability. Please contact your sales agent if you would like to book this.&nbsp;</span></h3>\r\n', '', '', '', '[]', '', '', '', '', '', '5 breakfasts, 4 lunches, 3 dinners', 'Boat, Private vehicle', 'Hotel (4 nights)\r\nCampsite (1 night)', '- Bolaven Plateau - Visit Tad Fane and Tad Lo waterfalls\r\n- Bolaven Plateau - Xe Pian tropical forest and to Phou Asa archaeological site trekking\r\n- Don Khong Island - Visit Khone Phapheng and Li Phi Falls', '', 0, 'lsp-panoramic-southern-laos', 'LSP - PANORAMIC SOUTHERN LAOS', 'Go on an adventure to discover the new routes, visit Laos plateau with lush coffee plantation, admire the dolphins on the Mekong River and peek in to the great culture through the unique temples of Laos.', 'southern Laos, Laos tour, Indochina tour, Greentours'),
