(53, 27, 'vn', 'LNJ - PLAIN OF JARS IN PHONSAVAN', 'Visit the Plain of Jars, a megalithic archaeological landscape in Laos, which was created by Mon-Khmer group whose culture remains a mystery of humanity  to this day.', '', '', '<h2 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\">Explore Phonsavan - The Plain of Jars</span></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Come and visit the Plain of Jars, a famous archaeological site in Phonsavan. The Plain of Jars is a megalithic archaeological landscape in Laos. It consists of thousands of stone jars scattered along the valley and central plains of Xieng Khuoang Plateau. Archaeologists believe that the jars in this field date back 1500 to 2000 years, created by people of the Mon-Khmer group. Mon-Khmer culture to this day remains a mystery of humanity.</span></p>\r\n', '<h3 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">1. Please provide your full name exactly as per passport at the time of booking (including any middle names listed on your passport).&nbsp;<br />\r\n2. A single supplement is available on this trip, subject to availability. Please contact your sales agent if you would like to book this.&nbsp;</span></h3>\r\n', '', '', '', '[]', '', '', '', '', '', '2 breakfasts, 1 lunche, 1 dinner', 'Private vehicle', 'Hotel (2 nights)', '- Xieng Khouang - Visit Buddhist sites, historic temples and caves\r\n- Phonsavan - Visit Plain of Jars, a megalithic archaeological landscape', '', 0, 'lnj-plain-of-jars-in-phonsavan', 'LNJ - PLAIN OF JARS IN PHONSAVAN', 'Visit the Plain of Jars, a megalithic archaeological landscape in Laos, which was created by Mon-Khmer group whose culture remains a mystery of humanity  to this day.', 'Plain of Jars tour, Laos tour, Indochina tour, Greentours'),
