(61, 31, 'vn', 'LGV - GOLF GETAWAY IN VIENTIANE', 'This Laos golf tour will bring unforgettable experience for golf enthusiasts to explore the exquisite golf courses and indulge yourself in the peaceful landscapes. Here you can also enjoy a high-class life and relax after a busy day.', '', '', '<h2 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\">Golf Getaway in Vientiane Package</span></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Laos, the country known as &quot;the land of millions of elephants&quot; embraces in itself plenty of secrets that enrapture many travellers.&nbsp;You will have the opportunity to explore the most beautiful golf courses in Laos such as Long Vien Golf Club, built by Long Thanh Golf Company (Vietnam) with 557 hectares wide and is considered to be the largest and most modern golf course in Vientiane at present. Or at 80 km away from Vientiane, the picturesque and poetic Dansavanh Golf &amp; Country Club lying on the banks of Nam Ngum Lake will bring unforgettable experience for golf enthusiasts. Come to Laos to experience the exquisite golf courses, explore the peaceful landscapes and indulge yourself in nature. Here you can also enjoy a high-class life and relax after a busy day.</span></p>\r\n', '<h3 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">1. Please provide your full name exactly as per passport at the time of booking (including any middle names listed on your passport).&nbsp;<br />\r\n2. A single supplement is available on this trip, subject to availability. Please contact your sales agent if you would like to book this.&nbsp;</span></h3>\r\n', '', '', '', '[]', '', '', '', '', '', '4 breakfasts', 'Private car, taxi', 'Hotel ( 4 nights)', '- Lakeview Vientiane Golf Club\r\n- Dansavanh Golf Club\r\n- Long Vien Golf Club', '', 0, 'lgv-golf-getaway-in-vientiane', 'LGV - GOLF GETAWAY IN VIENTIANE', 'This Laos golf tour from Greentours Indochina wi