(65, 33, 'vn', 'CGS - CAMBODIA STAY & PLAY', 'Playing at the leading golf courses while learning about the ancient Khmer history, this Cambodia golf tour is the perfect combination of sport and culture. Greentours Indochina will be your best choices in making your trip an amazing time with both your family and your partners.', '', '', '<h2 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\">Cambodia Stay &amp; Play&nbsp;Package</span></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Cambodia is known as a peaceful and hospitable country which still retains the old style of the French colonial architecture. Golfing in Cambodia has been developing strongly, attracting many tourists to come here to experience the unique world-class golf courses. Playing at the leading golf courses along with learning and experiencing the ancient Khmer history is the perfect combination of sport and culture, and Greentours Indochina will be your best choices in making your trip an amazing time with both your family and your partners.</span></p>\r\n', '<h3 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">1. Please provide your full name exactly as per passport at the time of booking (including any middle names listed on your passport).&nbsp;<br />\r\n2. A single supplement is available on this trip, subject to availability. Please contact your sales agent if you would like to book this.&nbsp;</span></h3>\r\n', '', '', '', '[]', '', '', '', '', '', '8 breakfasts, 2 lunches', 'Private car, taxi', 'Hotel (8 nights)', '- Play a round of golf at Garden City Golf Club\r\n- Full day Phnom Penh city tour\r\n- Play a round of golf at Vattanac Golf Resort\r\n- Play a round of golf at Phokeethra Country Club\r\n- Full day tour in Angkor Complex\r\n- Play a round of golf at Angkor Golf Resort', '', 0, 'cgs-cambodia-stay-play', 'CGS - CAMBODIA STAY & PLAY', 'Playing at the leading golf courses while learning about the a