(71, 36, 'vn', 'VLCG - INDOCHINA GOLF TOUR', 'If you are an entrepreneur looking for an opportunity to experience golf combined with cultural exchange, join a local golf tournaments or open up opportunities for cooperation, Greentours Indochina is undoubtedly at the top of your choices to offer specially designed and tailored golf tours as per your requests to conquer the challenging golf courses, ', '', '', '<h2 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\">Golfing&nbsp;in Vietnam, Laos and Cambodia</span></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">If you are an entrepreneur looking for an opportunity to experience golf combined with cultural exchange, or local golf tournaments arrangement to enhance the connection between business people to open up opportunities for cooperation and development in the future, Greentours Indochina is undoubtedly at the top of your choices. Your golf tours are carefully&nbsp;designed and organized for you to conquer the challenging golf courses. High quality services will be tailored to your wishes and budgets so that you can have the best time with your family and partners while golfing not only in Vietnam but also in Laos and Cambodia.</span></p>\r\n', '<h3 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">1. Please provide your full name exactly as per passport at the time of booking (including any middle names listed on your passport).&nbsp;<br />\r\n2. A single supplement is available on this trip, subject to availability. Please contact your sales agent if you would like to book this.&nbsp;</span></h3>\r\n', '', '', '', '[]', '', '', '', '', '', '21 breakfasts, 8 lunches', 'Private vehicle, Taxi', 'Hotel (21 nights)', '- Luang Prabang Golf Club\r\n- Lao Country Club\r\n- Lakeview Vientiane Golf Club\r\n- Long Vien Golf Club\r\n- Tam Dao Golf Resort\r\n- FLC Ha Long Bay Golf Club\r\n- Laguna Lang Co Golf Club\r\n- KN Golf Links Cam Ranh\