(73, 37, 'vn', 'VSB - GRAND VIETNAM EXPLORATION', 'Join the exclusive Vietnam tour to experience the century-old architectures, rich culture, magnificent natural landscape and luscious unique tastes of traditional delicacies from North to South with this tour package from Greentours Indochina.', '', '', '<h2><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\">Journey to&nbsp;the in-depth culture of Vietnam</span></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Join the exclusive trip where you will have a chance to experience the&nbsp;hundred-year-old architectures and rich culture of Vietnam. Indulge yourself in the luscious unique tastes of traditional and local delicacies.&nbsp;Trek the mountainous trails to ethnic minorities&#39; villages to learn about the indigenous traditional customs. Board the cruise to relax in a tranquil trip through the sea and river. Enjoy the luxury stay in the&nbsp;most modern and busy cities in Vietnam.</span></p>\r\n', '<h3 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">1. Please provide your full name exactly as per passport at the time of booking (including any middle names listed on your passport).</span></h3>\r\n\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">2. A single supplement is available on this trip, subject to availability. Please contact your sales agent if you would like to book this.&nbsp;</span></h3>\r\n\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">3. This trip includes flight trips. Checked luggage allowance is a maximum 20kg, with up to 7kg carry on luggage. Any excess luggage charges will need to be paid directly to the airline at check-in.</span></h3>\r\n', '', '', '', '[\"2019-11-10\"]', '', '', '', '', '', '11 breakfasts, 5 lunches, 3 dinners', 'Private vehicle, Boat', 'Hotel (11 nights)', '- Hanoi - Exciting city tour with a number of attractions\r\n- Halong - Crusing in the natural wonder of the world\r\n- Hue - Cruising along the quixotic Perfume River\r\n- Hoi An - Visit the cultural heritage of the ancient town\r\n- Ho Chi Minh City - The central hub of southern Vietnam\r\n- Mekong Delta - Cruising through the Mekong river', '', 0, 'vsb-grand-vietnam-exploration', 'VSB - GRAND VIETNAM EXPLORATION', 'Join the exclusive Vietnam tour to experience the century-old architectures, rich culture, magnificent natural landscape and luscious unique tastes of traditional delicacies from North to South with this tour package from Greentours Indochina.', 'Vietnam tour, Greentours, Indochina tour'),
