(75, 38, 'vn', 'VNF - NORTHERN VIETNAM FAMILY TOUR', 'Explore rich history and culture in ancient Hanoi capital, trek through green terraced rice fields and ethnic minority villages in Sapa and enjoy a luxury cruise trip on Ha Long Bay with Greentours Indochina', '', '', '<h2><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\">Fantastic trip in northern Vietnam with your family</span></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">This 8-day-vacation is well designed for your family to visit the most attractive destinations in northern Vietnam. Your family will have chance to explore rich history and culture of the thousand-year-old capital of Vietnam, trek through terraced rice fields and villages and learn about culture of minority ethnic groups in Sapa and lastly enjoy cruise trip through karst cave and islets&nbsp;in Ha Long Bay - one of Nature Wonder of the World. Let&lsquo;s take this trip and create&nbsp;memorable experiences with your loved ones.</span></p>\r\n', '<h3 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">1. Please provide your full name exactly as per passport at the time of booking (including any middle names listed on your passport).<br />\r\n2. A single supplement is available on this trip, subject to availability. Please contact your sales agent if you would like to book this.&nbsp;<br />\r\n4. An airport arrival transfer is included. Please provide your flight details at the time of booking.</span><br />\r\n&nbsp;</h3>\r\n', '', '', '', '[]', '', '', '', '', '', '7 breakfasts, 5 lunches and 1 dinner', 'Private car, bus, cruise', 'Hotel ( 6 nights)\r\nCruise ( 1 night)', 'Hanoi - City tour\r\nSapa - Trekking through villages and visit ethnic people\r\nHa Long - one night on cruise and visit Sun World park\r\n', '', 0, 'vnf-northern-vietnam-family-tour', 'VNF - NORTHERN VIETNAM FAMILY TOUR', 'Explore rich history and culture in ancient Hanoi capital, trek through green terraced rice fields and ethnic minority villages in Sapa and enjoy a luxury cruise trip on Ha Long Bay with Greentours Indochina', 'Northen Family tour'),
