(77, 39, 'vn', 'VSF - FAMILY TRIP IN SOUTHERN VIETNAM', 'Enjoy bustling atmosphere in Ho Chi Minh city, amazing underground system of Cu Chi Tunnels, a fascinating boat trip along Mekong river and delicious food in Southern Vietnam with Greentours Indochina', '', '', '<h2 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\">Exciting family trip in Southern Vietnam</span></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">This trip to Southern Vietnam will bring your family interesting experience in the life time. You will visit most of attractions in the bustle and hustle Ho Chi Minh, discover underground system of Cu Chi Tunnels and enjoy special cuisine and street foods of the city.&nbsp; Spending 2 days in Mekong delta with full of excitement, you will experience a boat trip along Mekong river, through mazes of canals to observe the vibrant atmosphere at the floating market then visit rural villages and orchards, meet friendly local and feel peaceful atmosphere .</span></p>\r\n', '<h3 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">1. Please provide your full name exactly as per passport at the time of booking (including any middle names listed on your passport).<br />\r\n2. A single supplement is available on this trip, subject to availability. Please contact your sales agent if you would like to book this.&nbsp;<br />\r\n4. An airport arrival transfer is included. Please provide your flight details at the time of booking.</span><br />\r\n&nbsp;</h3>\r\n', '', '', '', '[]', '', '', '', '', '', '5 breakfasts, 4 lunches', 'Private car, bus, boat', 'Hotel (5 nights)', 'Ho Chi Minh city - City tour\r\nHo Chi Minh - Cu Chi tunnels, Suoi Tien Theme Park\r\nMekong - Sightseeing, boat trip, floating market', '', 0, 'vsf-family-trip-in-southern-vietnam', 'VSF - FAMILY TRIP IN SOUTHERN VIETNAM', 'Enjoy bustling atmosphere in Ho Chi Minh city, amazing underground system of Cu Chi Tunnels, a fascinating boat trip along Mekong river and delicious food in Southern Vietnam with Greentours Indochina', 'Southern Family tour'),
(78, 39, 'en', 'english version VSF - FAMILY TRIP IN SOUTHERN VIETNAM', 'english version ', '', '', 'english version ', '', '', '', '', '[]', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 0, 'en-vsf-family-trip-in-southern-vietnam', 'VSF - FAMILY TRIP IN SOUTHERN VIETNAM', '', ''),
(79, 40, 'vn', ' VFH - FASCINATING VIETNAM FAMILY HOLIDAY', 'Endowed with numerous breathtaking natural landscapes, grandiose mountains and highlands as well as crystal blue beaches, Vietnam promises to be a wonderful destination for your family’s holiday.', '', '', '<h2><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\">Enjoy breathtaking landscapes and meet warm people in Vietnam&nbsp;</span></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Endowed with numerous breathtaking natural landscapes, grandiose highlands and mountains, crystal emerald beaches, Vietnam is a promising destination for your family&rsquo;s holiday. &nbsp;With this tour, you will go through most must-see attractions across the country, which give you chance to see historical sites with thousands of preserved&nbsp;relics and antiques, learn about rich culture and local&rsquo;s life, enjoy cruise trip at one of the Wonders of the Word, taste quintessential cuisine of the country and emerge yourself in beautiful sandy long beaches. A lot of fun activities and distinctive experience in each region will satisfy your children&rsquo;s curiosity.</span></p>\r\n', '<h3 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">1. Please provide your full name exactly as per passport at the time of booking (including any middle names listed on your passport) for flight tickets.<br />\r\n2. A single supplement is available on this trip, subject to availability. Please contact your sales agent if you would like to book this.&nbsp;<br />\r\n3. This trip includes a domestic flight. Checked luggage allowance is a maximum 20kg, with up to 7kg carry on luggage. Any excess luggage charges will need to be paid directly to the airline at check-in.<br />\r\n4. An airport arrival transfer is included. Please provide your flight details at the time of booking.</span><br />\r\n&nbsp;</h3>\r\n', '', '', '', '[]', '', '', '', '', '', '12 breakfasts, 7 lunches and 1 dinner', 'Private car, cruise, airplane, bike, boat.', 'Hotel (11 nights)\r\nCruise (1 night)', 'Hanoi - City tour\r\nHa Long Bay - cruise trip and Sunworld Park\r\nHoi An - sightseeing and Farming and Fishing Life Tour \r\nNha Trang - Island tour\r\nHo Chi Minh - City tour, Cu Chi tunnels\r\nMekong delta - Boat trip', '', 0, 'vfh-fascinating-vietnam-family-holiday', ' VFH - FASCINATING VIETNAM FAMILY HOLIDAY', 'Endowed with numerous breathtaking natural landscapes, grandiose mountains and highlands as well as crystal blue beaches, Vietnam promises to be a wonderful destination for your family’s holiday.', 'Vietnam family tour'),
