(95, 48, 'vn', 'MY SON SANCTUARY DAY TOUR', 'My Son Sanctuary is an extremely unique architectural complex of Champa temples and is recognised by UNESCO as the only evidence of a once existed civilization in Asia.', '', '', '<h2><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\">My Son Sanctuary - The once forgotten&nbsp;treasure</span></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Situated 70 km to the southwest of Da Nang,&nbsp;My Son Sanctuary is an architectural complex of Champa temples with extremely unique architecture. Forgotten for centuries, it was not discovered in 1885 and in 1999 this place was selected by UNESCO as a world heritage as the only evidence of a once existed civilization in Asia.</span></p>\r\n', '<h3 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">1. Please provide your full name exactly as per passport at the time of booking (including any middle names listed on your passport).&nbsp;<br />\r\n2. A single supplement is available on this trip, subject to availability. Please contact your sales agent if you would like to book this.&nbsp;</span></h3>\r\n', '', '', '', '[]', '', '', '', '', '', 'Not included', 'Private car, bus', 'Not included', '- Visit the mysterious ancient Champa architectural complex', '', 0, 'my-son-sanctuary-day-tour', 'MY SON SANCTUARY DAY TOUR', 'My Son Sanctuary is an extremely unique architectural complex of Champa temples and is recognised by UNESCO as the only evidence of a once existed civilization in Asia.', 'My Son Sanctuary tour, Da Nang, Hoi An, Vietnam tour, Greentours Indochina'),
