(97, 49, 'vn', 'BANA HILL DAY TOUR', 'Immerse in the natural landscapes, savour all the food and enjoy the festive atmosphere with lots of activities to keep you entertained all day at Bana Hills!', '', '', '<h2 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\">Bana Hills - The road to heaven</span></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Come&nbsp;to Bana Hills and experience four seasons in a day. Hop on the cable cars and&nbsp;immerse in the natural landscape of the endless primeval forests in Nui Chua. Savour a variety of cuisines and enjoy the festive atmosphere. There are a whole lot of activities to keep you entertained all day, from&nbsp;the exciting Fantasy Park - the largest indoor amusement park in Vietnam with various entertaining and active games for the whole family - to the Dinosaur Park - a destination not to be missed if you are a fan&nbsp;of the series &quot;Jurassic Park&quot;. Here also lies the first wax exhibition in Vietnam with wax statues modelled after many famous people in the world.</span></p>\r\n', '<h3 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">1. Please provide your full name exactly as per passport at the time of booking (including any middle names listed on your passport).&nbsp;<br />\r\n2. A single supplement is available on this trip, subject to availability. Please contact your sales agent if you would like to book this.&nbsp;</span></h3>\r\n', '', '', '', '[]', '', '', '', '', '', '1 lunch', 'Private car, bus', 'Not included', '- Visit Bana Hills - the most significant resort and recreational complex of Vietnam', '', 0, 'bana-hill-day-tour', 'BANA HILL DAY TOUR', 'Immerse in the natural landscapes, savour all the best food and enjoy the festive atmosphere with lots of activities to keep you entertained all day at Bana Hills!', 'Bana Hills tour, Da Nang, Vietnam tour, Greentours Indochina'),
