(109, 55, 'vn', 'MKC - EXPLORE MEKONG DELTA BY BIKE ', '', '', '', '<h2><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\">Enjoy rustic Mekong Delta on wheels</span></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<h1 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Along with boat trip, cycling is one of the best ways to feel authentic Mekong delta. Our local guide will lead you through quiet roads, green paddy fields, peaceful villages and orchard gardens. It is great chance to admire scenic landscapes, enjoy fresh atmosphere, meet and greet friendly local people as well as taste unique local cuisine.</span></h1>\r\n', '<h3><span style=\"font-size:18px\">1. Please provide your full name exactly as per passport at the time of booking (including any middle names listed on your passport).<br />\r\n2. Bicycle hire is included in your trip price. Please advise your height at time of booking so as we can organise a suitable sized bike.</span></h3>\r\n', '', '', '', '[]', '', '', '', '', '', '2 breakfasts, 3 lunches, 1 dinner', 'Van, bike, boat, ferry', 'Hotel ( 2 nights)', 'Cai Be -  sampan boat and visit villages\r\nVinh Long - visit craft industries\r\nCan Tho - Cai rang floating market', '', 0, 'mkc-explore-mekong-delta-by-bike', 'MKC - EXPLORE MEKONG DELTA BY BIKE ', 'Cycling is one of the best ways to feel authentic Mekong delta. You \'ll ride pass green paddy fields, visit peaceful villages, orchard gardens and meet friendly locals.', 'Mekong Delta cycle'),
