(111, 56, 'vn', 'VSPN - SOUTHERN VIETNAM BEACH RELAXATION', '', '', '', '<h2><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\">Immerse yourself in stunning beaches in Southern</span></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">With over 3,000km of coastline, Vietnam possesses&nbsp;so many beautiful beaches. Some of the best&nbsp;are found in the southern of the country. In this tour, you will have a chance to explore most highlights of vibrant Ho Chi Minh city then spend couple days relaxing and enjoying crystal clear water,&nbsp;fresh air, blue bays, swaying palms,&nbsp;white sand, sunshine&nbsp;on the beaches in Mui Ne and Nha Trang and take part in a lot of water activities. For beach lovers or those seeking for refreshment after hard work, this trip is all you need.</span></p>\r\n', '<h3 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">1. Please provide your full name exactly as per passport at the time of booking (including any middle names listed on your passport).<br />\r\n2. A single supplement is available on this trip, subject to availability. Please contact your sales agent if you would like to book this.&nbsp;<br />\r\n3. For 1 pax, you will be on a shared limousine or bus from Ho Chi Minh city to Mui Ne and from Mui Ne to Nha Trang. If you want a private car, surcharge will be applied.</span><br />\r\n&nbsp;</h3>\r\n', '', '', '', '[]', '', '', '', '', '', '6 breakfasts and 1 lunch', 'Private car, bus, jeep', 'Hotel (6 nights)', 'Ho Chi Minh - city tour\r\nMui Ne - Sand dunes tour\r\nNha Trang - unwind at the beach', '', 0, 'vspn-southern-vietnam-beach-relaxation', 'VSPN - SOUTHERN VIETNAM BEACH RELAXATION', 'Pristine beaches, crystal water, fresh air, blue bays, swaying palms, white sand, sunshine and a lot of \r\ninteresting water activities, all of which you can find in this tour.\r\n', 'Southern Vietnam beach'),
