(73, 'English and Korean Sales Tour Inbound ', 'Enthusiastic and engaged persons who are willing to join our Inbound sales team in Hanoi. The applicants can speak English or Korean well, looking to work with international clients, in a great and friendly multi-cultural company.\r\n\r\n', '<h2>JOB DESCRIPTION</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Understand all company&#39;s tour programs.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Revise and update tour programs</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Receive clients&#39; request via email, hotline or other means of communication then answer, advise and persuade them to buy our tours.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Making calculations and sending quotations to cliens</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Co-operating with the operation department&nbsp;to follow up and ensure the completion of the tour programs.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2>JOB REQUIREMENTS</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Fluent in English and Korean languages</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Creative, dynamic, good knowledge about products and destinations in Vietnam</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Good analytical and problem solving skills and strong decision making skillsls</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Good communication skills</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Good computer skills (Excel, Word, Outlook)</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Characteristics: pleasant personality, positive attitude, open-minded, honest, active, decisive</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">University: Bachelor or Master major in Hotel/Tourism/Foreign languages or other related fields</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">At least 1 year experience at the same position is a plus</span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2>WHAT WE OFFER</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Competitive &amp; attractive salary with bonus</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Equal rewards for individual devotion &amp; performance</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Working from Monday to Saturday morning&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Social &amp; health care insurance</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">The Thirteen Salary</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Training and traveling opportunities</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Joining anual company trip</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Public holiday bonus</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Marriage Gift</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Birthday Gift</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', NULL, '0', 0, '', '2019-09-30', '2019-12-25', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'English and Korean Sales Tour Inbound ', 'Due to the need to expand our business, Greentours recruits two more English and Korean speaking inbound sales staff who are enthusiastic and engaged persons who are willing to join our team in Hanoi.', 'english-and-korean-sales-tour-inbound', 'Recruitment Sales Inbound', 1),
(74, 'IT Support', '', '<h2>JOB DESCRIPTION</h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Providing adequate administration / maintenance activities for the system availability including.</span></p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Providing technical support to internal end-users and outside customers.</span></p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Planning, control and ensure the IT infrastructure &amp; information equipment.</span></p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Supporting the person in charge of IT related projects/tasks.</span></p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Taking care of security systems/functions: firewall, antivirus, etc.</span></p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Maintaining Server systems: Local server, file server, Application servers; repairing ICT hardware equipment.</span></p>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Troubleshooting, systems backups, archiving, and disaster recovery, etc..</span></p>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h2>JOB REQUIREMENTS</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>University: College degree in computer sciences or above;</li>\r\n	<li>Certifications: MCSA/MCSE, CCNA, Open sourcing expert is an advantage.</li>\r\n	<li>Experience: having at least 1 year of experience in network/system administration and end-user support activities</li>\r\n	<li>Experience in setting up and administering Microsoft platform based servers &amp; PCs is required</li>\r\n	<li>Office applications professional is required</li>\r\n	<li>Good understanding of large &amp; complex LAN /WAN Networks, Data Center Operations, backup,Disaster recovery, Antivirus with many different customized application software.</li>\r\n	<li>Motivation in IT and hopeful for a stable job;</li>\r\n	<li>Responsible, accurate and able to work under high pressure and to strict deadlines.</li>\r\n	<li>Good teamwork skills, communication &amp; interpersonal skills</li>\r\n	<li>English fluently is an advantage</li>\r\n	<li>Characteristics: Pleasant personality, positive attitude, open-minded</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>WHAT WE OFFER</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><em><strong>*** Total rewards:&nbsp;</strong></em><br />\r\nIn addition to the handsome salary &amp; bonus under the working capacity, you are committed to working in dynamic working environment with featured policy and benefits as below:<br />\r\n<em><strong>1. Training:&nbsp;</strong></em></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Specific knowledge: You will be offered intensive training with inspection trips in destinations which makes you confident with the knowledge &amp; real experience to consultant more effectively to customers.</li>\r\n	<li>Skills: In low seasons, along with English course annually, several skills training courses are organized to make you have opportunity to practice &amp; self &ndash; improve abilities.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><em><strong>2. Benefits</strong></em></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Motivation trips: Under the spirit&rdquo; Work Hard, Play Hard&rdquo;, annually there will be several Motivation trips of the whole Company, of each department, each destination with a lot of attractive team building, which enhance the team spirit and explore the potential ability of staff. In Head Office, there will be some short motivation trips giving you unforgettable experiences of interesting activities, such as: trekking, hiking, biking, kayaking,&hellip;</li>\r\n	<li>Along with annual health check &ndash; up once a year, Company also offer a pack of comprehensive health insurance &amp; accident insurance 24/24 AON.</li>\r\n	<li>Greentours Indochina&nbsp;also pays attention to the spiritual life of each staff on special occasions like birthday, wedding, Women Day, Mid &ndash; Autumn for children,&hellip;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>The details about benefits as below:</p>\r\n\r\n<p><em><strong>Working time</strong></em></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>40 hours per week (8h&nbsp;&ndash; 11:30h &amp; 13h30 &ndash; 17h30)</li>\r\n	<li>Off on Saturday &amp; Sunday</li>\r\n	<li>12 days of annual leave entitlement</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><em><strong>Benefit &amp; Advantage:</strong></em></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Staff Wellness Program:</li>\r\n	<li>Annual Medical Checkup</li>\r\n	<li>Personal accident and health insurance 24/24 (AON)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><em><strong>Company Events:</strong></em></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Motivation Trip</li>\r\n	<li>Year End Party</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><em><strong>Other extras:</strong></em></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Lunch allowance</li>\r\n	<li>Public holiday bonus</li>\r\n	<li>Business bonus</li>\r\n	<li>Thirteenth-month salary</li>\r\n	<li>Marriage Gift</li>\r\n	<li>Birthday Gift</li>\r\n	<li>Education: English classes with a Native English teacher (tuition free)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', NULL, '0', 5, '', '2019-11-01', '2019-12-25', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'IT Support', '', 'it-support', 'Employing IT Supporter - Greentours Indochina', NULL),
(75, 'Marketing trainees - Training from A - Z', '', '<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#e74c3c\">Students !! What have you prepared for the future ???</span></span></strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">In 2017, Vietnam received&nbsp;additional 200,000 unemployed bachelors, the rest after graduation almost accept to work as &quot;temporary&quot; jobs that are not in the right profession or not very popular. The reason is that most students nowadays are too absorbed in learning knowledge at universities but forget about practical experience at companies and businesses. Therefore, before the employer&#39;s question: &quot;What experience have you had in this position&quot;, Almost reply falteringly.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#e74c3c\">How about you? If you are:</span></span></strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">&nbsp;An enthusiastic and dynamic young person who lacks practical work experience?</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">&nbsp;Coming out of school but still very vague about what I&#39;m really good at?</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">&nbsp;Have aspirations, wills and efforts but have not found an appropriate environment to devote?</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">➡</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">️</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">➡</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">️</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">➡</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">️ Come&nbsp;to the Marketing team of Greentours. Do not save your&nbsp;youth to prepare for unemployment !!!</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#e74c3c\">What will you get when participating in MARKETING PRACTICE at GREENTOURS?</span></span></strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">You will learn 4 topics for free with direct guidance from the Leader, Particularly:</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">SEO website: Standard SEO article writing skills, set up SEO keyword industry cover up to 10,000 keywords, guide the entire process of keyword SEO to TOP 1-2-3 in just 3-6 months.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">Writing PR - Advertising: A guide to the whole formula of writing&nbsp;articles according to the most updated concepts with a very attractive title on social networks.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">Google Adwords</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#e74c3c\">At the same time:</span></span></strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">Asked about any issues related to Marketing.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">Feel free to express yourself, contribute ideas to the leadership.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">Consideration for official work if done well.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">Flexible practice schedule according to your schedule (minimum 4 sessions / week).</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">The environment is&nbsp;comfortable, eating and drinking, lunch and compensation are always worth the effort.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt\"><span style=\"color:#e74c3c\">What is your job at Greentours?</span></span></strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">===&gt; Support Marketing team in advertising campaigns, organizing events&nbsp;and work under instruction of team leader.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">Join our Marketing team now to experience the HOT industry today</span></span></p>\r\n', NULL, '0', 5, '', '2019-11-01', '2019-12-25', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Marketing trainees - Training from A - Z', '', 'marketing-trainees-training-from-a-z', '', NULL),
(77, 'Visa Counselor', 'Due to the need to expand Visa business, Greentours recruits two more visa counselors.', '<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:20px\"><strong><span style=\"color:#c0392b\">Job description:</span></strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Receiving requirement from customers.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Processing documents: Translating, filling in forms, consulting customers, supporting customers to book airline tickets, hotel...</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Following the process of completing visa applications.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Receiving feedback and solve problems if happened, answering customers inquiries, sending info to relate departments.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Other jobs are assigned by superiors.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:20px\"><strong><span style=\"color:#c0392b\">Request:</span></strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Active, flexible, patient, confident. Service thought. Ability to work independently</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Preferably graduated from college, major in Economics, Commerce and Tourism. Candidates who have worked in the same position, or in the field of travel, air tickets</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Good communication and negotiation skills.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:20px\"><strong><span style=\"color:#c0392b\">Working environments:</span></strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Working in a professional environment with 19 years establishment.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Individually instructed by seniors.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Work hard play hard, eat and drink all week. Friendly and fun colleagues.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Reward for exceeding the work targets. A chance to be the head of the department based on work result.</span></p>\r\n', NULL, '0', 5, '', '2019-11-02', '2019-12-25', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Visa Counselor', 'Recruiting to work in Greentours Indochina', 'visa-counselor', '', NULL);

